var book = {
	"name": "2 Samuel",
	"numChapters": 24,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Saul a thih hnuah David cu Amalek ral a nehnak ihsin a ra kir ih Ziklag khua ah ni hnih a um.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> A thaisun ah Saul thihnak hmun ihsin tlangval pakhat a ra thleng. A riahsiat ruangah a hnipuan a thlek ih a lu ah leivut a phulh aw. David hnenah a feh ih leilung dai in upatnak pekin a lu a kun.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Cutikah David in, “Khuitawk inso na rat?” tiah a sut. Anih in, “Israel ralkap pawl lakin ka ra tlan,” a ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Ziang an cang, i sim hnik,” tiah David in a ti. Cutikah tlangvalpa cun, “Israel ralkap pawl cu an tlan thluh ih tampi an thi fawn. Saul le a fapa Jonathan khal an thi,” tiah a ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Saul le Jonathan an thi, tiah ziangtinso na theih?” tiah David in a sut sal.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Tlangvalpa in, “Gilboa tlang parah ka rak um ve ih an ral pawl rangleng le rang ralkap pawl in an hun naih vivo ih culaiah Saul cu a feipi pawk in a din kha ka hmu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> A her-aw ih keimah i hmu ih i ko. “Bawipa, ziangso?” tiah ka ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> “Zoso na si?” tiah i sut ih, “Amalek mi ka si,” tiah ka ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cutikah, “Besiazet in in tuahmawh zo ih ka thi cing ding. Ra awla i ra that aw,” tiah i ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Curuangah a umnak ah ka hung so ih ka that, ziangahtile a tlu ding ih a tluk vete cun a thi thotho ding, ti ka thei. Cun a lu parih a siangpahrang lukhuh le ralnam khamnak baanhrolh cu ka lak ih atu na hnenah ka rak keng a si, bawipa,” tiah a ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> David cu riahsia le ninghang in a hnipuan a thlek thluh ih a milai pawl hmuahhmuah khal in an thlek thluh ve.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> An ṭaang cuum aw in an ṭap ih, Bawipa ih minung Israel mi tampi ralih an thih ruangah le Saul le Jonathan tla an hlohral ruangah zan tiang rawl ul in an um.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cule David in hi thu a ra simtu tlangvalpa cu, “Khuilam mi so na si?” tiah a sut. “Amalek mi ka si naón na ram sungah hin ka um,” tiah a sawn.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> David in, “Ziangtin so Bawipa in siangpahrang ih a hril mi cu na thah ngam?” tiah a ti ih,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> a ralkap pakhat ko tahratin, “Hi pa hi that aw,” tiah thu a pek. Curuangah ralkap pa cun Amalek tlangvalpa cu a sah thluk ih a that.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cutikah David in, “Na thisen cu na lu parah tlaseh. Bawipa Pathian in siangpahrang ih a hrilmi ka that a si, tiah na hmurka rori ih na phuan ruangah nangmah le nangmah na nunnak na cemter-aw a sihi,” tiah Amalek pa cu a ti.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> David in Saul le a fapa Jonathan cu hla in a ṭah ih,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> a cuih hla cu Judah mi pawl ih zir dingin thu a pek. (Hi thihhla cu Jashar Cabu sungah an ngan.)",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Maw mi vanduai Israel bawi pawl, Nan ram tlangmual ih nan thih hi, Ralṭha hleice pawl vanduai ni a suah hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Gath khua ah va sim hlah uh, Ashkelon khua ih lamzin ah phuang hlah uh; Filistin nunau an lung a awi pang ding. Khawvel fanu pawl an di a riam tuk pang ding.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Maw Gilboa tlang, Na parah ruah le dai khal tla hlah seh, Na leiram cu caar le kolh in thlairawl zianghman suah hlah seh! Ziangahtile ralṭha pawl ih ralphaw cu a rop duahdo ih, Saul ih ralphaw cu a tlap ṭheh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Jonathan ih li le thal cu mi hriamah a hmual a na, Saul ih ralnam cu mizaangfah a nei lo. Micak zet pawl khal a ṭhio thluh ih, Ral pawl khal a saattan thluh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Maw Saul le Jonathan, Nan duh awknak mangbangza a si; Nunnak ah nan hmun khat ih thihnak khalah nan hmunkhat; Muvanlai hnakin nan rangdeuh, Kiosa hnakin nan cakdeuh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Maw Israel nunau pawl, Saul cu ṭah cio uh; Hnipuan mankhung sunglawi in, sen thliaithliai ih a lo thuamtu amah a si; Hlawnthil mankhung le suingun in a lo mawitertu amah a si.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ral ṭha hleice ralkap pawl an van a duai ee, Raldonak ah an hloral ta; Tlang parah Jonathan cu a thita.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Maw Jonathan, ka unau duh, nangmah ruangah ka riah a sia, Ziangtluk duhnungza so ka hrangah na si! I duhdawtnak cu ziangtluk mangbangza so a si, Nunau ih duhdawtnak hnakin a thlum sawn.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kan miṭha pawl an ral zo, An hriamnam pawl khal an hloral thluh zo,” tin a ṭah."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cuih hnuah David in, “Judah ramih khua pakhatkhatah ka hung feh pei maw?” tiah Bawipa a ron. “Feh aw,” tiah Bawipa in a ti. Cule David in, “Khui khua ah so ka feh ding?” tiah a sut sal. Cutikah Bawipa in, “Hebron ah feh aw,” tiah a ti.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Curuangah David cu a nupi pahnih, Jezreel khuami Ahinoam le Nabal ih thihsanmi Karmel khuami Abigail thawn Hebron ah a feh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> A milai ralkap pawl le an innsang pawl khal a fehpi ih Hebron khua ah a um.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cule Judah mi pawl Hebron khua ahcun an ra ih Judah siangpahrang ah David cu hriak an culh. Gilead ramih Jabesh khuami pawl in Saul cu an phum ti kha David in a theih tikah,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> mi a thlah ih, “Nan bawipa Saul parah upatnak nan nei ih ṭhatein nan rak phum ruangah Pathian in lo thlawsuah hram seh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bawipa cu nan parah zaangfah thinpemnak a neimi le rinsantlak ringringmi Pathian si hram seh. Hi bangtuk ih nan tuah ruangah keimah khal in ka lo zoh ṭha ve ding.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cak uhla nan ralṭha uh. Nan siangpahrang Saul cu a thi ih atu ah keimah cu Judah mi pawl in an siangpahrang sinakah hriak in culh zo a si,” tiah thu a cah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ner ih fapa Abner, Saul ralkap hotu cu, Saul ih fapa Ishbosheth thawn an tlan ih Jordan tiva khatlam ral Mahanaim ah an va thleng.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cutawkah Abner in Ishbosheth cu siangpahrang ah a canter ih Gilead, Asher, Jezreel, Efraim le Benjamin ram le Israel ram pumpi a uk.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Siangpahrang a can tikah Ishbosheth cu kum 40 a si ih kum hnih sung a uk. Sikhalsehla Judah miphun cun David an ṭan ih,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> David in Judah mi pawl cu Hebron khua ihsin kum sarih le a hrek sung a uk.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Abner le Ishbosheth ralkap pawl cu Mahanaim ihsin an pok ih Gibeon khawpi ah an feh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Joab, (a nu cu Zeruiah a si), le David ralkap pawl cu Hebron ihsin an pok ih Gibeon khua ah an feh ve. Gibeon khua ih tili kapah an tong aw. Abner le a ralkap pawl cu tili kap khatah ṭanhmun an khuar ih Joab le a ralkap pawl cu khatlam kapah ṭanhmun an khuar ve.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cule Abner in, “Kan tlangval pawl hrekkhat suak veve in pakhat le pakhat tawng aw hai sehla a ṭha ding,” tiah Joab cu a ti. Cule Joab in, “Sihen seh!” a ti.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Curuangah Ishbosheth le Benjamin phun ai-awh ah minung hleihnih an suak ih David ih milai pawl ai-awh ah hleihnih an suak ve.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> An do awk tikah mahih hmaton ral kha an lu in an kai ih an thinhna ah an ralnam in an dawt aw ih hmunkhat ah an zatein an tlu ih an thi thluh. Curuangah Gibeon khua kiang a cuih hmun cu Helkath-hazzurim “Ralnam Hmun,” tiah an kotata.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cutikah do awknak nasa zetin a um ih Abner le Israel mi pawl cu David ralkap pawl in an neh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Zeruiah ih fapa pathum Joab, Abishai le Asahel tla an pathum in an tel. Cule zukneng tlukih tlan a cakmi Asahel in,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Abner cu a dawi ih khuadang tang loin a dawi vivo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cutikah Abner cu dunglam a rak hoi ih, “Asahel maw na si?” tiah a ti. “A si, Asahel ka si,” tiah a sawn.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Abner in, “I dawi nawn hlah aw. Ralkap pakhatkhat dawi sawn awla a kenmi long sawn aw,” a ti. Asinain Asahel cun a dawi thotho.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cule Abner in, “I dawi nawn aw hlah! Ka lo that ngaingai ding sokhaw. Ka lo thah asile ziangtinso na u Joab mithmai ka zoh ngam nawn ding?” tiah a ti.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Asinain Asahel cun a dawi cu a bang cuang lo. Curuangah Abner in a feipi cu dungkhawh in a khawh ih Asahel cu a thinhna ihsin a zaang ah tlang ko in a khawh ngah. Asahel cu a sawn ih a thi. Cule Asahel ruak umnak an thlen tikah zozo khal an cawl ih cutawkah an ding.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Sikhalsehla Joab le Abishai in Abner cu an dawi sal ih ni a tlak cuarco ah Giah ihsin nisuahnak lam, Gibeon ramlak fehnak lamzin ih a ummi Ammah tlang an thleng.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Benjamin mi pawl cu Abner hnenah an finkhawm aw sal ih tlangpar ahcun ṭanhmun an khuar.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Cule Abner in Joab cu a auh ih, “Hitiin maw kumkhua kan do awk rero ding? A netnak ahcun huat awk sinsinnak lawng a suak ding, tihi na thei lo maw si? Kannih tla hi na phunpi rori kan si! Na minung pawl in kanmah in dawi hi dawn loin maw na um men ringring ding?” tiah a ti.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Cutikah Joab in, “Cuvekin hung ṭongsuak hlah cila, a nungmi Pathian hmin salin ka lo sim: ka ralkap pawl in thaizing tiang an lo dawi rero ko ding naón,” tiah a ti.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Cule Joab in tawtawrawt a tum ih a ralkap pawl in Israel mi pawl cu an dawi nawn lo. Curuangah an do awknak cu an bang.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Abner le a ralkap pawl cu Jordan tivakap phairawn ah zanvar an feh ih, Jordan tiva an tan hnuah a thaisun sunhlan an feh ih Mahanaim an thleng.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Abner an dawi nawn lo hnuah Joab in a ralkap pawl cu a khawm ih Asahel tel loin hleikua an thi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> David ralkap pawl ih an thah mi Benjamin mi, Abner ralkap pawl cu zathum le sawmruk an si.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Joab le a ralkap pawl in Asahel ruak cu an zawn ih Bethlehem khua, an innsang thlaan ah an phum. Cule zanvar an feh ih a thaizing zingpit ah Hebron an thleng sal."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Saul ih sungkhat pawl a ṭantu ralkap pawl le David le a ralkap pawl cu reipi an do-aw ringring. David cu ni khat hnu ni khat a cak deuhdeuh ih a ral pawl cu ni khat hnu ni khat an ṭawnṭai vivo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hebron ih a suakmi David fapa pawl cu a hnuailam pawl hi an si. Pakhatnak cu Amnon a si ih a nu cu Jezreel khuami Ahinoam a si.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> A pahnihnak cu Khileab a si ih a nu cu Nabal ih thihsan mi, Karmel khuami Abigail a si. A pathumnak cu Absalom a si ih a nu cu Geshur ram siangpahrang Talmai ih fanu Maakah a si.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> A palinak cu Adonijah a si ih a nu cu Haggith a si. A panganak cu Shefatiah a si ih a nu cu Abital a si.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> A paruknak cu Ithream a si ih a nu cu Eglah a si. Hi fapa pawl cu Hebron ih suakmi an si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Saul sungkhat a ṭantu ralkap le David ralkap pawl an do awknak a rei vivo tikah Saul sungkhat ṭantu ralkap pawl sungah Abner cu thuneitu a si deuhdeuh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nikhat ah Saul ih fapa Ishbosheth in Abner cu Saul ih nupisun Aiah ih fanu Rizpah thawn an ittlang a si, tiah sual a puh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cutikah Abner cu a thin a heng ngaingai ih, “Mi phiartu ah maw i ruat? Judah riantu ah maw i ruat? A hramthok ihsin na pa le a unau pawl le a rualpi pawl hnenah a ṭang ringringtu ka si ih, David ih kut sungah ka lo thlenter dah lo. Cuti asinain tuih ni ah nunau thawn sual i puh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hi ram cu Saul le a tesinfa pawl hnenih sin ka lak pei ih David cu Israel le Judah ram, khatlam zim Dan ihsin khatlam zim Beersheba tiang, uk thluhtu siangpahrang ah ka canter ding, tiah Bawipa Pathian in David cu a tiam zomi a si. Cuvek ih ka tuahsuak lo asile Pathian in i that seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ishbosheth in Abner cu a ṭih tuk ih kam khat hman a sawn ngam lo.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Culai ah David cu Hebron ah a um ih a hnenah Abner in palai a thlah ih, “Hi ram hi zo in so a uk cuang ding? Keimah thawn lungkimnak cakhen tuah awla Israel ram na neh thluhnak dingah ka lo bawm ding,” tiah a cah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cutikah David in, “A ṭha! Lungkimnak ka tuah pei. Asinain ka hnenih na rat tikah Saul ih fanu Mikhal na rak hruai lawnglawng ah kan tuah thei ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cun Ishbosheth hnen khalah David in palai a thlah ih, “Ka nupi Mikhal i pe sal aw. Amah co dingah a man ah Filistin mi zakhat ih vunzim ka pek a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Curuangah Ishbosheth in Mikhal cu Laish ih fapa a pasal Paltiel hnen ihsin a hruai sal.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Paltiel cun a nupi Mikhal cu a sian lo tuk ruangah a ṭap thluahthlo ih Bahurim khua tiang a thlun. Cutikah Abner in, “Kir thlang aw,” a ti ih Paltiel cu a kir.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Abner cu Israel mi hotu pawl hnenah a feh ih, “David nan siangpahrang si dingih nan duhnak cu a reipi zo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Atu hi nan hrangah tikcu ṭha bik a si. Bawipa Pathian in, ‘Ka salpa David ka hmang pei ih ka minung Israel pawl cu Filistin pawl le an ral dang pawl kut sung ihsin ka run ding,’ tiah a timi kha nan thei thluh ko,” a ti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Abner cu Benjamin mi pawl khal thu a sim phah vivo ih, cuih hnuah Israel le Benjamin mi pawl ih lungkimnak sim dingah Hebron ah David hnenah cun a feh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hebron ih David hnenah cun Abner cu minung kul thawn an feh ih David in an hrangah rawl ei puai a tuahsak.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cule Abner in David hnenah, “Maw siangpahrang bawipa, ka va feh pei ih Israel ram cu a zatein na uknak sungah ka ratpi ding. An siangpahrang ah an lo pom ko ding. Cuticun na lungthlitum cu na ngah ding ih hi ram cu a pumpi in na uk ding a si,” tiah a ti. Abner cu David in hnangamte in a fehter.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cuih hnuah Joab le David ih ralkap pawl cu mi an va siimnak ihsin an rakir ih hransaw thil an lakmi pawl tampi an rak keng. Abner cu himte in David in a thlah zo ruangah Hebron ah a um nawn lo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Joab le a ralkap pawl an thlen tikah Abner cu David siangpahrang hnenah a ra ih himte in David in a kuat sal zo, tiah an rak sim.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Cutikah Joab cu David hnenah a feh ih, “Ziang so na rak tuah? Na hnenah Ebner a ra ih ziangtinso cutimen in na fehter?",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Nangmah bum duh ah le na fehnak hmuahhmuah le na tuahmi hmuahhmuah hliah duh ah na hnenah a ra a si ti na thei lo maw?” tiah a ti.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> David hnen ihsin a feh hnuah Abner hruai dingah Joab in mi a thlah ih, Sirah tikhur ihsin an rak kirpi sal. A cuih thu cu David in zianghman a thei lo.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Abner cu Hebron an thlenpi tikah thuthup sim ding bangin kotka kiangah Joab in a hruai ih a thinhna ah a sun ih a thi. Cuticun Joab in Abner cu a that, ziangahtile a naupa Asahel a rak thah zo ruangah a phu a lak a si.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> A cuih thu David in a theih tikah, “Ka milai pawl le kei cun Abner an thahnak thu cu kan thei hrimhrim lo a si, ti cu Bawipa Pathian in a thei.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> A thisen cu amah Joab le a innsang parah thleng seh. Sankhat hnu sankhat, Joab ih sungkhat hnenah thisen sungdok nat maw, phaarnat maw, a si lole mahte feh thei loin kianghrol thawn a feh mi maw, raldonak ih a thimi maw, a si lole rawl eiding khopkham nei lo mi maw, um ringring hai seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Gibeon ih an do awknak ah Abner in an nau Asahel a rak thah ruangah Joab le a nau Abishai in Abner an thahnak cu a si.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Curuangah David in Joab le a milai pawl cu an hnipuan thlek tahrat in buri hnipuan hruk ih Abner ṭah dingah thu a pek. Cun an phum tikah ruak kuangih dungah David siangpahrang cu a ke rori in a feh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Abner cu Hebron ah an phum ih a thlaan ah David siangpahrang cu napi in a ṭap. Mi hmuahhmuah khal an ṭap ṭheh.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> David cun hla in a ṭah ih: “Mi aa bangin Abner na thi maw si?",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na kut an lo ṭem lo, Na ke tla an lo khit lo; Misual pawl ih thahmi na bang hi,” a ti. Mi hmuahhmuah khal in an ṭah sal.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ni a tlak hlanah ziangtal ei dingah David cu a minung pawl in an fial rero naón a duh lo. “Nitlak hlanih ziang maw ka ei hnak cun Pathian in i that sawnseh,” tiah thu a kam.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Cutiih a ti cu senpi in an hmuh tikah an lung a kimzet. Siangpahrang ih thil a tuahmi hmuahhmuah cu an lungkim zawng a si thluh.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Abner ih lu hlohnak ah hin siangpahrang a tel lo a si, ti cu David ih milai pawl le Israel mi hmuahhmuah in an thei.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Cun David in a kuthnuai bawi pawl hnenah, “Tuihsun ah Israel ram hruaitu ṭha le mimak pakhat a thi, tihi nan thei maw?",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Keimah cu Pathian ih hrilmi siangpahrang ka si naón tuihsun cu ka thin a nau ngaingai a si. Hi Zeruiah fapa pawl cu ka hrangah tuar an har tuk. Anmah ih tuah vekin hi misual pawl parah Pathian in hremnak thlenter hram seh,” tiah a ti."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hebron ah Abner an that a si, ti kha Saul fapa Ishbosheth in a theih tikah a thin a phang ngaingai ih Israel mi hmuahhmuah khal an thin a nuam lo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Midang an siim tikih an hotu bawi pahnih Ishbosheth in a nei ih an hmin ah Baanah le Rekhab an si. Anmah cu Benjamin miphun, Beeroth khua Rimmon ih fapa an si. Beeroth cu Benjamin ram sungah siarcih a si.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Beeroth ih a rak um hmasatu pawl cu Gittaim ah an tlan ih cutawk minung ah an cangta.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cun Saul ih fapa Jonathan in fapa pakhat a nei ih a hmin cu Mefibosheth a si. Saul le Jonathan an thihnak thu Jezreel ihsin a ra than tikah Mefibosheth cu kum nga a kim. Amah a umtu nu in a lak ih a tlanpi. Asinain zamrang tukin a tlanpi ruangah a thlak pang ih Mefibosheth cu a ke pahnih in a bai ta.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Rekhab le Baanah cu Ishbosheth ih inn lamah an feh ih sunah an va thleng. Ishbosheth cu sunih a colh laifang a si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> A sangka kiltu nunau nu cu sangvut a hrik rero laiah a ih a hmu ih a it that. Cutiih a ihthat laiah Rekhab le Baanah cu a thupte in an vung lut.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Innsung an thlen vete in Ishbosheth ihnak khaan sungah an lutih a ihthat laifangah Ishbosheth cu an sun ih an that. A lu an tan ih an lak hnuah zanvar Jordan Phairawn in an feh ih Hebron khua ah an thleng.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ishbosheth ih lu cu David hnenah an fehpi ih a hnenah, “A lo raltu le a thah a lo tumtu Saul ih fapa Ishbosheth ih lu cu hihi a si. Tuihsun ah Bawipa Pathian in Saul le a tesinfa pawl parih phulaknak cu siangpahrang na hnenah a lo pek a si,” tiah an ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cutikah David in, “Ṭihphannak hmuahhmuah sung ihsin i runtu a nungmi Bawipa ih hmin in siat ka serh a si!",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ziklag ah ra tahrat in Saul ih thihnak thu i ra simtu cun thuṭha ka phur tiah a ruat. Asinain amah cu ka kai ih ka that. Thuthang a rak ken ruangih hlawhman ka pekmi cu thih a si.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Mawhnak nei lomi amah ih inn sungih a it lai mi rori a va thattu misual pawl ih hrangah cun ziangtlukin so a har sinsin ding. Ishbosheth nan thah ruangah atu rori ah nan parah phu ka lak ding ih lei parah hin nan ci ka hmit thluh ding,” a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> David in thu a pekih a ralkap pawl in Rekhab le Baanah cu an that ih an kut le an ke pawl an tan ih Hebron ih tili kiangah an thlai. Cun Ishbosheth ih lu cu an lak hnuah Hebron ahcun Abner ih thlaan ah an phum."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Israel miphun pawl hmuahhmuah cu Hebron ih David hnenah an ra ih, “Kannih cu na thi le na sa kan si.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kan dunglai ih kan siangpahrang Saul a rak si laiah, Israel mi pawl cu raldonak ah na hruai ih, Amah Pathian rori in a minung pawl tuukhal bangin kilkhawitu dingah le uktu dingah a lo kam a si,” tiah an ti.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Curuangah Israel mi hotu pawl hmuahhmuah cu Hebron khua David hnenah cun an ra. Pathian hmaika ah David in anmah thawn thukamnak a tuah ih Israel siangpahrang ah David cu hriak an culh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> David cu siangpahrang a can tikah kum sawmthum a si ih kum sawmli sung siangpahrang a ṭuan.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hebron ihsin Judah ram cu kum sarih le a hrek a uk ih, Jerusalem ihsin Israel le Judah ram zatein kum sawmthum le kum thum a uk a si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> David le a ralkap pawl cu Jerusalem khua nam dingin an feh. A cuih khua ih a rak ummi Jebus mi pawl in David cun in neh dah lo ding, tiah an ruat ih, “Na lut thei dah lo ding; mitcaw le kebai mi khal in an lo kham thei ding,” tiah an rak ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Sikhalsehla David in Zion khua ih ral pawl an ṭannak ruhkulh cu a lak ṭheh ih Zion khua cu David ih khawpi ah a cangta.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cuih sunah David in a milai pawl hnenah, “Jebus mi pawl ka huat tlukin a huatu nan um maw? Kan thah thluh le a tawk nan ti maw? Tiluannak kua ah hung feh uhla mitcaw le kebai mi pawl tiangin hung that thluh uh,” tiah a ti. Curuangah, “Mitcaw le kebai mi pawl cu Bawipa ih inn ah an lut thei lo ding,” tiih an tinak a si.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cule ral ṭannak ih an sakmi ruhkulh a lak hnuah David cu cutawk ah a um ih, “David ih Khawpi,” tiah hmin a sak. Millo an ti mi hmun ihsin a thok ih ral ṭannak a dawl vivo ih cuih khua kimvel in a dawl ṭheh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ziangkimtithei Bawipa Pathian cu a hnenih a um ruangah David cu ni khat hnu ni khat a cak vivo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ṭaiar siangpahrang Hiram in an ram ai-awh in David hnenah palai a thlah ih David ih inn saknak dingah sidar thing tla a kuat. Inn saktu dingah zungthiam pawl le lung inn dawlthiamtu pawl tla a kuat.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Curuangah Israel siangpahrang ah Bawipa Pathian in i nemhnget zo a si, ti le a minung Israel pawl ih ruangah a uknak cu a ṭhansoter a si, ti kha David in a theifiang a si.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hebron ihsin Jerusalem ih a ṭhawn hnuah David in Jerusalem ah nupi le nupisun pawl tam sinsin a nei ih fanu le fapa tampi a nei.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Jerusalem ih a hrinmi a faale pawl cu Shammua, Shobab, Nathan, Solomon,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ibhar, Elishua, Nefeg, Jafia,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Elishama, Eliada le Elifelet tla an si.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> David cu Israel siangpahrang a cang zo, ti kha Filistin mi pawl in an theih tikah an ralkap zatein an pok ih David kai dingah an feh. David in cuih thu a theih tikah ral ṭannak ruhkulh innah a vung feh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Filistin ralkap pawl cu Refaim Phairawn timi an thleng ih cutawk cu an luah.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Cutikah David in, “Filistin pawl hi ka do pei maw? Ka do asile ka neh pei maw?” tiah Bawipa a sut. Bawipa in, “Feh awla do aw. Nehnak ka lo pe ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Curuangah David cu Baal Perazim ah a feh ih Filistin pawl cu a neh. “Tilian bangin Bawipa in ka ral pawl cu a pah suak a si,” tiah David in a ti. Curuangah a cuih hmun cu Baal Perazim  tiah an ti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Filistin pawl in an milem pawl an tlansan thluh ruangah David le a ralkap pawl in an lak ṭheh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cule Filistin ralkap pawl cu Refaim Phairawn ah an ra kir sal ih an luah sal.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> David in Bawipa cu a ron sal ih Bawipa in, “Hitawk ihsi cun na do lo pei. Heel awla an dunglam in balsam  thingkung pawl umnak kiang ihsin rak nam hai aw.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Thingkung zim parah ke feh thawm na theih asile hmakhatte-ah nam hai aw. Ziangahtile Filistin ralkap pawl neh dingah na hmaiah Bawipa Keimah ka feh zo tinak a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> David in Bawipa ih sim vekin a tuah ih Filistin ralkap pawl cu an tlan ih Geba ihsin Gezer tiang a dawi hai."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> David in Israel ralkap lakih a ṭha bik pawl a khawm ih thawng sawmthum an kim.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cherub pahnih karlakih a siangpahrang tokham parih a to Ziangkimtithei Bawipa ih hmin an putter mi Thukam Kuang la dingah acuih ralkap pawl cu a hruai ih Judah ram Baalah khua ah an feh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Thukam Kuang cu cawleng thar parah an ret ih tlang parih Abinadab ih inn ihsin an suahpi. Abinadab ih fapa Uzzah le Ahio in Thukam Kuang a phurtu cawleng cu an kilkhawi phah vivo.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cawleng hmaiah Ahio a feh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cule Bawipa ih hmaiah an lungawi in hla an sak ih tingrisit, ṭingṭang, khuang, mumeek le darsumsel pawl an tum ih David le Israel mi pawl cu an laam thei patawp in an laam ciamco.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cule Nakon ih fang cilnak puum an thlen tikah leng hnuktu cawcang cu an bah ih curuangah Uzzah in a hei dawh ih Thukam Kuang cu a kai ngah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cutikah Bawipa Pathian ih thinhengnak cu Uzzah parah meisa bangin a alh ih cutiih ṭihzahnak a neih lo ruangah Uzzah cu Thukam Kuang kiangah cun a thihter.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bawipa a thin a heng ruangah Uzzah a that a si, ti kha David in a theih tikah a ai a thok ih a cuih hmun cu Perez Uzzah  tiah an ko. Tuihsun tiangin cuticun an ko ta.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cule David in Bawipa cu a ṭih ih, “Ziangtin so atu-ah Thukam Kuang cu ka ken ngam ding?” tiah a ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Curuangah amah ih khua Jerusalem ah fehpi lo dingin a ruat. Git khua ih ummi Obed Edom ih innah a fehpi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cutawkah Thukam Kuang cu thlathum a um ih Bawipa in Obed Edom le a innsang pawl cu mal a sawm.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Thukam Kuang an inn ih a um ruangah Obed Edom le a innsang pawl le a neihmi hmuahhmuah cu Bawipa in mal a sawm, ti kha David in a theih tikah Thukam Kuang cu Jerusalem ih ken dingah lungawi le thatho zetin Obed ih inn ihsin a lak.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cule Thukam Kuang a phurtu pawl kar ruk an kar tikah David in Bawipa ih hnenah cawcang pakhat le a thau mi tuu faate pakhat thawinak ah a pek.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cun David cu puan nemte pakhat lawng a thlaih ih Bawipa thangṭhatnak ah a laam thei patawp in a laam ciamco.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cutiin David le Israel mi pawl in au phah le mumeek tum phah in Thukam Kuang cu Jerusalem khua an thlenpi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Thukam Kuang Jerusalem khua sungih a thlen tikah, Saul ih fanu Mikhal in sangkate in khua a hei zoh ih David cu Bawipa ih hmaiih a laam le a khir rero kha a hmuh tikah David parah a mitkem ngaingai.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> David ih sak ciami Puanthlam sungah Thukam Kuang cu an rak keng ih an ret. Cuih hnuah David in mei-ur thawinak le remnak thawinak Bawipa ih hnenah a pek.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Thawinak pawl a pek ṭheh hnuah Israel mi pawl cu Ziangkimtithei Bawipa ih hminin thluasuah a pe hai.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Cun nunau siseh, mipa siseh sang zawlkhat ciar, a ro ih kiomi sa semkhat ciar, le caarmi sabit rah hlom khat ciar a zem hai. Cuih hnuah misenpi cu an inn ciarah an tlung.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Amah David khal a innsang tong dingin a tin ve ih Saul ih fanu, a nupi Mikhal in a rak hmuak ih, “Tuihsun Israel siangpahrang cu a hmin a thangzet ual! A hnaṭuantu fala pawl hmaiah mi aa bangin puan paate thawn ningzah hman thiam loin a laam ciamco kha!” tiah a rak ti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cutikah David in, “A minung Israel mi hruaitu ah i tuah ih na pa le a sungkhat pawl lan tahratin keimah sawn i hriltu Bawipa Pathian sunloihnak ah ka laam a si. Bawipa sunloihnak ahcun ka laam rero ko ding ih,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> mualpho sinsin khal ka si ko ding. Nang cun zianghman ah i siar lo ding, asinain na timi fala pawl cun in uar zet ding a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Saul ih fanu Mikhal cu a thih tiang faate a nei lo."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> David siangpahrang cu ral nei loin ram uktu a si ih a siangpahrang inn ah daitein a um ngah tikah,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Profet Nathan hnenah, “Zohhnik, kei ka umnak hi sidar thingih sakmi inn a si ih, Pathian ih Thukam Kuang sawn cu thlam sungih ret a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Cutikah Nathan in, “Tuah na duhmi cu tuah aw. Bawipa na hnenah a um a si,” a ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Sikhalsehla a cuih zan ah Bawipa in Nathan hnenah,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “David ka salpa hnenah va feh awla, ‘Ka umnak dingah biakinn a saktu ding cu nangmah na si lo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Israel mi pawl Izipt ram in ka suahpi ihsin tuihsun tiang biakinn sungah ka um dah lo. Ka fehnak kipah puanthlam sungah ka um ringring.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Israel mi pawl thawn ka fehnak hmuahhmuah ah Israel hotu dingih ṭuanvo ka pekmi hruaitu pawl hnenah, ziangah so ka hrangah sidar thingih biakinn nan sak lo, tiah ka ti dah lo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Curuangah David cu sim awla Keimah Ziangkimtithei Bawipa ih ṭongmi cu hiti in a si: Ka minung Israel mi pawl hruaitu dingah nangmah cu hramlakih tuu na khalhnak ihsin ka lo ko.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Keimah cu na fehnak hmuahhmuahah ka tel ih na ral pawl ka neh thluh. Cule leilung tlunih mi tum bik tlukin mi hminthangzet ah ka lo tuah ding.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ka minung Israel hrangah hmun ka hril ding ih cutawkah zohmanih hnaihnok nawn loin an um ding. Hi ram an thlen thok ihsin anmah cu mi puarthau pawl in an do ringring. Sikhalsehla cuticun a si nawn lo ding. Na ral pawl hnen ihsin ka lo hum ding ih tefa sin tampi ka lo pe ding, tiah thu ka lo kam.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na nunnak a cem ih na pu le na pa hnenah phum na si tik khalah na fapa pakhat cu siangpahrang ah ka tuah ding ih a ukmi ram cu ka cakter ding.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ka hrangah biakinn a sak pei ih a tefa sin pawl ih ram an uknak cu kumkhua in a hmun ding.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Keimah cu a pa ka si ding ih amah cu ka fapa a si ding. Sualnak a tuah tik khalah a pa in a fapa cu nun a sim ṭheu vekin amah cu nun ka sim ding. Milai in nunsimnak ah fungfeek an hman bangin ka hmang ding.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sikhalsehla a hnen ihsin ka duhdawtnak cu ka lakir lo ding. Nangmah siangpahrang na sinak dingih Saul hnen ihsin ka duhdawtnak ka lakkir vek cun ka lakir lo ding.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Tesinfa na nei vivo ding ih na uknak cu a kumkhua in ka hmunter ding. Na siangpahrang uknak cu a cem dah lo ding,’ tiah va sim aw,” tiah a ti.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Pathian in a hnenih a run phuan mi hmuahhmuah cu Nathan in David hnenah a sim thluh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cutikah siangpahrang David cu Bawipa umnak Puanthlam ah a feh ih a to ih thla a cam: “Maw Bawipa Pathian, kei hi zianghman ka si lo! Ka hrangih thil na tuah mi hmuahhmuah co dingah ka tlak hrimhrim lo. Ka innsang pawl khal an tlak lo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bawipa Pathian, hi hnakih tam deuh khal na tuah lai ding a si. Hmailam tikcu ih ka tesinfa pawl hrangah thukamnak na tuah zo. A cuih thu cu, maw Bawipa, ka hnenah na fiangter zo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Maw Pathian, lo dil ding zianghman a um nawn lo. Na salpa kei hi i thei thluh ko.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hi thil hmuahhmuah hi na tuahmi le na tummi an si. Hi tlukih mangbangza thil hi nangmah in i theiter thluh zo.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Maw Bawipa Pathian, ziangtluk mangbangza so na si? Nangmah bangtuk zohman an um lo; kanmah rori ih kan theih thluh zo vekin nangmah bangtuk Pathian zohman an um lo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Nangmah ih minung si dingih na run zomi Israel mi vek leilung tlunah zo miphun hman an um lo. Nangmah in na hmin cu na thanter ih na minung pawl hrangah thil maksak le mangbangza tampi na tuah a si. Mi phundang pawl le an khawzing pawl cu na minung pawl lamzin tluangter dingah na dawihlo ṭheh. Israel mi pawl cu na ta si dingah Izipt ram ihsin na luatter zomi an si.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na miphun Israel pawl cu kumkhua in na minung ah na tuah ih Bawipa Nangmah cu an Pathian na si zo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> “Curuangah Bawipa Pathian, keimah le ka innsang hrangih na thukammi hmuahhmuah cu a kumkhua in kimter hram awla, ka tuah ding na timi cu tuah thluh ko aw.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na hmin cu kumkhua in a thang ding ih mi in, ‘Cungnungbik Bawipa cu Israel uktu Pathian a si,’ tiah an ti ding. Cun ka tesinfa pawl cu cat loin siangpahrang siter hram aw.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Cungnungbik Bawipa, Israel ih Pathian, ka tesinfa pawl siangpahrang an si ringringnak ding cu keimah na salpa hnenih na langter zo ruangah na hnenih ral ṭhazet in thla ka cam ngamnak a si.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Maw Bawipa Pathian, nang cu Pathian na si ih, na thukammi cu na kimter ringring. Ka hnenah hitluk ṭha thukamnak na tuah zo.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Curuangah Bawipa, na mithmai ṭha cotu an si ringringnak dingah ka tesinfa pawl cu nangmah in atu-ah thlawsuahnak pe hram aw. Bawipa Pathian, nangmah in hi thukamnak cu na tuah zo ih ka tefa pawl ih parah na thlawsuahnak cu a kumkhua in um hram seh,” tiah a ti."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> David in Filistin pawl cu a neh ih Filistin mi pawl ih an ukmi ram pawl khal a long thluh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cun Moab mi pawl khal a neh ih a kaihmi pawl cu leilung parah a bawhter ih hridai in a tah hnuah milai ṭhenthum ih ṭhenhnih cu a that ih ṭhenkhat cu a zuah. Cutiin Moab mi pawl cu David ih kuthnuai ah an um ih ngunkhuai an pek.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Cule tlunta Eufrates Tiva kiangkap ih ram pawl neh kir duh ih a feh zawng ah Zobah ram siangpahrang, Rehob ih fapa Hadadezer cu David in a do ih a neh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> David in Hadadezer ih rang ralkap thawngkhat zasarih le ke ralkap thawng kul a kai ih leng hnuktu rang pawl cu an kaiza tha a sat cat thluh. Rangleeng zakhat hnuk khop ding lawng a zuah.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cun Damaskas khua ih Siria ralkap pawl cu Hadadezer bawm dingin an ra ih ralkap thawng kul hluanhnih cu David in a rak that.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Siria ram sungah ralkap a ret ih a kuthnuai minung ah an tla ih ngunkhuai an pek. A fehnak kipah Bawipa in David cu ral nehtu a siter.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hadadezer siangpahrang ih ralbawi pawl ih kenmi sui ralphaw pawl cu David in a lak ih Jerusalem ah a fehpi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hadadezer ih ukmi Betah le Berothai khawpi pawl ih sin dar tampi khal a lak.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hadadezer ih ralkap hmuahhmuah cu David in a neh thluh, ti kha Hamath khua siangpahrang Toi in a theih tikah,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> a fapa Joram cu David cibaibuk ding le lungawipi dingah David hnenah a thlah. David ih a nehmi Hadadezer cu siangpahrang Toi in voi tampi a rak do zomi a si. Curuangah Joram cun sui le ngun le dar ih tuahmi khukheng pawl David laksawng pe dingah a keng.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> David in khukheng pawl cu Pathian biaknak ih hman dingah a pek. Cun Edom ram, Moab ram, Ammon ram, Filistin ram le Amalek ram pawl a nehnak ihsin a lakmi sui le ngun le,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Zobah siangpahrang Hadadezer hnen ihsin a lakmi thilri sunglawi hrekkhat pawl khal Pathian hnenah a pek a si.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> David cu Cite Phairawn ih Edom mi thawng hleiriat a thahnak ihsin a ra kir tikah a hmin a thang sinsin.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Edom ram sungih hmun tampi ah ralkap a ret ih Edom mi pawl cu a kuthnuai minung ah an cang. Khawzakip ah Bawipa in David cu nehtu a siter.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> David in Israel ram pumpi cu a uk ih a minung pawl cu remte in le dingtein a uk a si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Zeruiah ih fapa Joab cu a ralkap pawl hotu a si. Ahilud ih fapa Jehoshafat cu cazin kaitu a si.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ahitub ih fapa Zadok le Abiathar ih fapa Ahimelek cu puithiam an si. Seraiah cu zung cazi a si.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> David siangpahrang kiltu Kereth mi le Peleth mi pawl a hotu cu Jehoiada ih fapa Benaiah a si. David ih fapa pawl cu puithiam an si."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ni khatah David in, “Saul ih sungkhat ihsin a nungmi pakhat tal an um maw? An um asile Jonathan ih ruangah an parah zaangfahnak ka langter duh a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cutikah Saul ih hnen-um pakhat Ziba timi a um ih amah cu David hnenah an fehter. A feh tikah, David in, “Ziba na si maw?” tiah a rak sut. Ziba in, “Ka si bawipa,” tiah a ti.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> David siangpahrang in, “Pathian hnenih thu ka kam zo vekin Saul sungkhat pawl parah zaangfahnak langter ka duh a si; a nungmi pakhat tal an um lai maw?” tiah a sut. Ziba in, “Jonathan ih fapa pakhat a nungmi a um ih a ke a zeng,” tiah a ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> David in, “Khuiah so a um?” tiah a sut. Ziba in, “Lodebar khua, Ammiel ih fapa Makhir ih inn ah a um,” tiah a sim.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cutikah Jonathan ih fapa cu David in a ko.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Saul ih fasuan, Jonathan ih fapa Mefibosheth a rathlen tikah upat ṭihzahnak in David ih hmaiah a kun. David in, “Mefibosheth!” tiah a ko. Anih in, “Bawipa, hinah ka um!” tiah a hun ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cutikah David in, “Na thinphang hlah. Na pa Jonathan ih i duhdawtnak ruangah na parah zaangfahnak ka nei a si. Na pu Saul ih leiram hmuahhmuah cu ka lo pe kir thluh ding ih nangmah cu ka hnenah rawl na ei ringring ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cutikah Mefibosheth cu a lu a kun sal ih, “Bawipa, kei hi uico thicia hman ka tluk lo. Ziangah so hitluk ih i zaangfah lawmmam?” a ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cule siangpahrang David cun Saul ih hnen-um Ziba a ko ih, “Saul le a sungkhat pawl ih neihmi hmuahhmuah cu na bawipa Saul ih fasuan Mefibosheth hnenah ka pe thluh ding.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Nangmah le na fapa pawl le na hnen-um pawl in an leiram cu nan ṭuan pei ih na bawipa Saul ih sungkhat pawl ih ei dingah rawl nan khawm pei. Asinain amah Mefibosheth cu ka hnenah rawl a ei ringring ding,” a ti. (Ziba in fapa hleinga le hnen-um kul a nei.)",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cutikah Ziba in, “Siangpahrang na thupek mi vekin ka tuah thluh ding,” tiah a ti. Mefibosheth cu siangpahrang ih fapa vekin David hnenah cun rawl a ei ringring.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cun Mefibosheth in Mika timi fapa pakhat a nei. Ziba ih sungkhat pawl cu an zatein Mefibosheth ih hnen-um ah an cang.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cuticun a ke a zengmi Mefibosheth cu Jerusalem ah a um ih rawl cu siangpahrang hnen lawnglawng ah a ei."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tikcu a hung rei deuh tikah Ammon siangpahrang Nahash cu a thi ih a fapa Hanun siangpahrang ah a cang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cutikah David in, “A pa Nahash in ka parih upatnak le zaangfahnak a rak tuah zo bangin Hanun parah ka langter ve ding,” a ti ih a riahsiat hnemtu dingah mi a thlah.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Sikhalsehla a mithlah mi pawl an va thlen tikah Ammon mi hruaitu pawl in an siangpahrang Hanun hnenah, “Na riahsiat hnemtu dingah tiah David in hiti ih mi a rak thlah hi na pa an upat ruangah a si, tiah na zum maw? Si hrimhrim hlah! In neh duh ruangah kan khawpi ra zohhliah dingin thlingthlatu hitawk ah a rak thlah a si,” tiah thusia an forh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Curuangah David ih thlahmi palai pawl cu Hanun in a kai ih an khabe hmul kapkhat lam ciar a met hnuah an kor fualpi cu an taai ri in a tansak ih a thlah hai.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cuih thu David in a theih tikah a palai pawl tong dingin mi a thlah. Ziangahtile an ning a zak tuk ruangah a hnenah an ra ngam lo. Jerikho khua ih um dingin le an khabe hmul a cerhsal hnu lawngih ra tlung dingin thu a cah.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cutiin David an ral ih an canter kha Ammon mi pawl in an theih fiang tikah, Bethrehob le Zobah ihsin Siria ralkap thawngkul an hlang; Tob ralkap thawng hleihnih, le Maakah ram siangpahrang tla a ralkap thawngkhat thawn, an hlang.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> A cuih thu cu David in a theih tikah Joab cu a ralkap ṭha bik pawl thawn a thlah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ammon mi pawl cu an ra suak ih Rabbah khawpi vung luhnak ihsin ṭanhmun an rak khuar. Siria ralkap, Tob ralkap le Maakah ralkap pawl khal ramkip le hmun kip in Israel pawl cu an rak bawh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Joab in ral pawl in hmailam le dunglam in in do ding, ti kha a theih tikah Israel ralkap lakih a ṭha bik pawl a hril ih hmailam ih Siria ralkap pawl dotu dingah a ret.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> A ralkap dang pawl cu a naupa Abishai ih ho ah a ret ih Abishai cu Ammon mi pawl tawng dingah ṭanhmun a khuarter.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Joab in a nau Abishai hnenah, “Siria ralkap pawl in in nor deuh asile in ra bawm pei. Cun Ammon ralkap pawl in an lo nor deuh asile ka ra lo bawm ding.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Zianghman ṭih hlah aw! Kan minung pawl le kan Pathian ih khawpi pawl hrangah nasa tak in kan ṭang pei. A ṭhabik a timi cu Bawipa in tuah hram seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cutikah Joab le a ralkap pawl cun an nam ciammam ih Siria ralkap pawl cu an tlanhlo ṭheh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cule Ammon mi pawl in Siria ralkap pawl an tlan kha an hmuh tikah Abishai mithmuh ah an tlan ve ih an khawsungah an kir. Ammon mi an donak ihsin Joab cu a kir ih Jerusalem a thleng sal.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Israel pawl in in neh a si, ti kha Siria mi pawl in an theih tikah an ralkap hmuahhmuah cu an khawm sal.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Eufrates Tivapi ihsin nisuahnak lamih a ummi Siria mi pawl khal Hadadezer siangpahrang in a ko thluh ih Helam ah an ra ih Zobah siangpahrang Hadadezer ih ralkap pawl uktu ralbawi Shobak ih ho in an um.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> A cuih thu cu David in a theih tikah Israel ralkap pawl a ko khawm ṭheh sal ih Jordan Tiva an tan hnuah Helam lamah cun an feh. Siria ralkap pawl cu Halem ah David do dingin nasa zetin ṭanhmun an rak khuar. An do aw ciammam ih,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Siria ralkap pawl cu Israel pawl in an dawiṭek thluh. David le a ralkap pawl in Siria rangleng mawngtu zasarih le rang ralkap thawng sawmli an that ih, Siria ralbawipa Shobak khal an hriam ih cuih hmunah a thi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Siangpahrang Hadadezer kuthnuai ih a ummi siangpahrang dang pawl khal in Israel pawl in in neh a si, ti kha an hmuh tikah, Israel thawn rem awknak an tuah ih an kuthnuai um ah an cang. Cuih hnu cun Siria mi pawl in Ammon mi pawl cu an bawm ngam nawn lo."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ṭhal a hung suakih siangpahrang pawl ral an do tikcu a thlen tikah, David in Joab le a kuthnuai bawi pawl le Israel ralkap pawl cu ral do dingah a kuat. Ammon ralkap pawl an neh ih an khawpi Rabbah cu an kulh. Asinain David cu Jerusalem ah a rak um.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Nikhat zanlam ah David cu sunih a colhnak ihsin a tho ih a inn diphun parah a kai. Diphun parih a feh rero laiah nunau pakhat ti a kholh-awk laifang a hmu. Cunu cu mimawi ngaingai a si.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Curuangah zo a si ti theih duh ah mi pakhat a thlah ih Eliam ih fanu Hit mipa Uriah ih nupi Bathsheba a si ti a thei.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bathsheba va hruai dingah David in midang a thlah sal ih a hnenah an ratpi. Cule David cun a ihpi. (Bathsheba cu thlatin thii a neih mi nunau daan thianfainak a tuah ṭheh pekte a rak si.) Cuih hnuah a inn ah a tin.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cule nau ka keng a si, ti a theih tikah David hnenah thu a cah.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> David in, Joab hnenah mi a thlah ih, “Hit mi Uriah kha ka hnenah rak thlah aw,” a ti. Curuangah Joab in Uriah cu David hnenah a thlah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Uriah a thlen tikah David in ralkap pawl ih thu le an raldonak thu pawl a rak sut.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cule a hnenah, “Inn ah va tlung awla va cawl hrih aw,” tiah David in a ti. Uriah cu a tlungih a inn ah David in laksawng tla a kuat.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sikhalsehla Uriah cu a inn ah a thleng lo. Siangpahrang inn kotka ih siangpahrang kiltu pawl hnenah a riak.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> David in Uriah cu a inn ah a tlung lo, ti kha a theih tikah a ko ih, “Tikcu reipi hnuah na ra tlung sikhawh, ziangah so na inn ih na tlun lo?” tiah a sut.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cutikah Uriah in, “Israel le Judah ralkap pawl cu lamhlatzet ah raldo in deu sungah an um ih Thukam Kuang khal an hnenah a um. Ka bawipa Joab le a kuthnuai bawi dang pawl tla hramlak ah an riak a si. Culai fangah ziangtinso ei le in dingah le ka nupi hnenih it dingah ka inn ahcun ka tlun thei ding? Cuvek cu ka tuah hrimhrim lo ding, tiah siatcam in thu ka kam a si,” a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cutikah David in, “Tuih sun cu hitawk ah um awla thaisun ah ka lo kuat kir ding,” tiah a ti. Curuangah a cuih sun cu Jerusalem ah a um.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> A thaisun ah Uriah cu David in zanriah a dar ih zu ri koin a tulh. Asinain a cuih zan khal inn ah a tlung cuang lo. Amah ih puan sin in siangpahrang inn kiltu pawl hnen thotho ah a riak.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> A thaizing ah David in Joab hnenah ca a ngan ih Uriah ih kut in a kuat.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> A ca sungah cun, “Uriah hi ral a hrannak bik, hmailam bikah rak fehter aw. Cule dunglam ah siipsan awla ral pawl in that hai seh,” tiah a ngan.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Curuangah Ammon mi khawpi an kulhnak ih ral a hrannak bikah Uriah cu Joab in a fehter.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ral pawl cu khawsungih sin an ra suak ih Joab ih ralkap pawl thawn an do aw. David ih ralbawi pawl hrekkhat cu an that ih Uriah khal an that a si.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cule an do awknak thu cu Joab in David hnenah a than.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> A thlah mi pa ih hnenah, “Kan raldonak thu azateón na sim ṭheh tikah,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> siangpahrang cu a thin a heng men ding ih, ‘Ziangah so Ammon mi do dingah an khawpi naih tukah nan va feh? An khua kulhnak phar parih sin li le thal thawn in kap ding, ti nan thei lo maw si?",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Jerubbesheth ih fapa Abimelek an thahnak tla nan hngilh zo mawsi? Thebez khua ah nunau pakhat in phar par ihsin fang rialnak lungto tumpi a parah a run thlak ih a thi a si kha! Cuti asinain ziangah so phar kiang tukah nan feh?’ tiah a lo ti asile, ‘Na ralbawi, Hit mi Uriah tla an that a si, ti aw,” tiah a cah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> A thlahmi pa cu David hnenah a feh ih Joab ih thucah mi vekin a sim ṭheh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> David hnenah, “Kannih hnakin ral pawl cu an cak deuh ih an khawpi sungih sin an ra suakih khawleng ah kan do aw. Asinain an khua ih kotka tiang kan dawi kir.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Cule an ṭannak phar parih sin thal thawn in kapih bawipa, na ralbawi hrekkhat an thi, Uriah khal an that a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Cutikah David in cumi pa ih hnenah, “Joab cu va sim awla a thinnau hlah seh, ziangahtile raldonak ahcun zo a thi ding, ti sim a theih ual lo. Nasa deuh in an khawpi cu do-aw sehla lak suak rak tum seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Cule a pasal a thi ti kha Bathsheba in a theih tikah mithi ngai in a um.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> A mithi ngai a reh tikah David in mi a thlah ih siangpahrang ih inn ah an va hruai. Cutiin a nupi ah a cang ih fapa a hrin. Sikhalsehla David ih thil tuahmi parah Bawipa cu a lung a awi lo."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> David hnenah profet Nathan cu Bawipa in a thlah ih, “Khua pakhat ah mi pahnih an um; pakhat cu a lianzet ih pakhat cu a farah zet.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Milian pa cu caw le tuu tampi a nei ih,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> mifarah pa cu a lei copmi tuu faate pakhat lawng a nei. A cuih a tuu pakhatte cu ṭhatein a zoh ih a innsang ah amah le a faale pawl lakah a tlang ih a ṭhang vivo. Amah ih eimi rawl a pek ve ih, a khuathai ihsin tidai a inter ih a kawngpar rori ah a cawi ṭheu. A tuu cu a fanute tlukah a ruat.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Nikhat cu milian pa ih inn ah mikhual pakhat a ra thleng. A mikhual cu rawldo a duh naón a ṭilva pakhat thah ding hman a siang lo. Curuangah mifarah pa ih tuu neihsun cu a lak sak ih a mikhual pa cu rawl a do a si,” tiah a simter.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cutikah David cu a thin a heng ngaingai ih, “A nungmi Bawipa ih hmin salin ka sim: cu vek thil ṭha lo a tuahtu cu a thih a ṭul a si!",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cutluk ih mi zaangfah nei lo a si ruangah a lakmi cu let li in samsaal tengteng seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cutikah Nathan in David hnenah, “A cupa cu nangmah hi na si! Israel ih Pathian Bawipa in, ‘Saul ih kut sung ihsin ka lo humhim ih Israel siangpahrang ah ka lo canter.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Saul ih ram uknak ka lo pek; a nupi pawl tla ka lo pek. Cule Israel le Judah ramih siangpahrang ah ka lo tuah. Himi pawl hi a tawk hrih lo a si ahcun a let hnih in ka lo pe hrih ding naón!",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ziangah so ka thukham na thlun lo? Ziangah so hibangtuk thil ṭha lo hi na tuah? Ral donak ah Uriah na thihter. Ammon mi pawl na thahter ih a nupi cu na nupi ah na lak.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hitiin ka thukham na thlun lo ih Uriah ih nupi na ruk ruangah na tesinfa hrekkhat pawl cu sankhat hnu sankhat ah saarthih in an thi ringring ding.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na innsang sung rori ihsin vansaang ih a lo tuahtu ka suakter hrimhrim ding, tiah ka lo sim cia. Na nupi pawl ka lak ding ih na mithmuh rori ah mipa dang hnenih ka pek tikah na thei leh ding. Cupa cun sun khawvanglai rori ah na nupi pawl cu a sualpi hai ding.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Nang cun a thupte in sualnak na tuah; sikhalsehla Israel mi pawl ih hmuh thluh dingah na nupi pawl a sualpinak cu sun khawvanglai rori ah kei cun ka kimter ding,’ a ti a si,” tiah a sim.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cutikah David in, “Bawipa  ih hmaiah ka sual zo a si,” a ti. Cule Nathan in, “Bawipa  in a lo ngaithiam ih a thih cu na thi lo ding.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Sikhalsehla hiti ih thil ṭha lo na tuahnak ihsin Bawipa na hmuhsuamnak cu na langter zo ruangah na fa a thi ding,” a ti.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cuih hnuah Nathan cu inn ah a tlung. Uriah ih nupi in David fapa a hrin mi cu Bawipa in besia zetin a natter.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> David in a fapa damnak dingah Pathian hnenah thla a cam. David cu rawl zianghman a ei lo, zantinte in a innsung zial parah tho loin a it ringring.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> A kuthnuai ih bawi pawl in zial parih it loih tho dingah an leem rero naón a ngai duh hrimhrim lo. Anmah thawn khal zianghman a ei duh lo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Zarhkhat hnuah a fapa cu a thi ih a kuthnuai bawi pawl in an sim ngam lo. “A fapa a nunlai hmanah kan bia rero naón in sawn duh lo. A fapa a thih cu ziangtinso kan sim ngam ding? Amah le amah tla a tuahmawh-aw pang ding,” an ti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Pakhat le pakhat a thupte ih an biak awk rero kha David in a hmuh tikah ka fapa a thi zo a si ding, tiah a ruat ih, “Naute cu a thi maw si?” tiah a sut. “Asi, a thi,” tiah an sawn.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cutikah David cu zial ihsin a tho ih ti a kholh-aw, a sam a hriat ih a hnipuan a thleng. A feh ih Bawipa ih inn ah Pathian a biak. Cun a inn ah a kir ih rawl a tuahter ih an tuah ṭheh vete in a ei.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cutikah a kuthnuai bawi pawl in, “Ziangtin so a si, na faate a nunlai hmuah ah na ṭap rero ih rawl zianghman na ei lo. Asinain a thih vete cun na tho ih rawl na ei. Kan va thei theilo so,” tiah an ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cutikah David in, “Asi, ka fapa a nunlai ahcun rawl ka ul ih ka ṭap rero. Ka fapa thihter loin Bawipa in i zaangfah pei maw, tiah ka ruat.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Sikhalsehla atu cu a thi zo ih ziangah so rawl cu ka ulh nawn ding? Ka fapa cu kan nunter sal thei pei maw? Nikhat khat cu a hnenah ka feh ve leh ding, asinain anih cu ka hnenah a ra thei nawn lo ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Cule David in a nupi Bathsheba cu a hneem. An it khawm sal ih Bathsheba in fapa a hrin. A fapa cu David in Solomon tiah hmin a sak. Solomon cu Bawipa Pathian in a duhdawt ih,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Jedidiah tiah hmin sak dingin profet Nathan hnenah thu a pek; ziangahtile Bawipa in a duhdawt a si.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Cuih sungah Joab in Ammon mi pawl ih khawpi Rabbah cu a rak heng rero ih a neh zik thlang.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> David hnenah mi a thlah ih, “Rabbah cu ka heng rero ih atu ahcun an tidai suahnak dawhhna ka lak zo.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Curuangah ralkap rak khawm awla Rabbah khawpi cu ra do awla nangmah in ra neh aw. Culole hi khawpi hi ka neh ding ih a hmin cu ka hmin cuang in ka sak ding” tiah thu a cah.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Thu a cah vekin David in a ralkap pawl cu a khawm ih Rabbah khua cu a do ih a neh ngaingai.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Cuih an lakmi khawpi ahcun Molek an timi an khawzing lem a um ih a sui lukhuh cu pawng sawm sarih le pawng nga a tlai mi sui lukhuh a si. A cuih lukhuh sungah lungmankhung tla an um. David in a cuih lukhuh cu an milem par ihsin a lak ih amah ih lu parah a khum. Hransaw thilri dang tampi khal khawsung ihsin a lak.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Khawsung mi pawl cu a hruai hai ih, hluah le tupheng le hreitlung thawn hna a ṭuanter ih tlakrawh tla a tuahter. Ammon ram sungih khua dangmi pawl khal cuvek thotho in hna a ṭuanter. Cuih hnuah David le a ralkap pawl cu Jerusalem ah an kir."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Tikcu a rei vivo ih, David ih fapa Absalom in farnu pakhat Tamar timi a neih mi cu mimawi ngaingai a si. Cule David nupi dangih fapa pakhat Amnon in Tamar cu a ngai.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Amnon cu Tamar a ngaituk ruangah a na; ziangahtile a co theinak lamzin a um hrimhrim fawn lo tiah a ruat. Tamar cu fala him a si ih mipa zohman an tongter dah lo.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Amnon in rualpi pakhat a nei ih a hmin cu Jonadab a si ih David ih u Shammah ih fapa a si. Jonadab cu mi depde a si ih,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Amnon hnenah, “Siangpahrang ih fapa na si naón ni khat hnu ni khat riahsia ninghang in ka lo hmu. Ziangruangah so a si, i sim hnik aw,” a ti. Cutikah Amnon in, “Ka unau Absalom ih farnu Tamar ka ngai ruangah a si,” tiah a sim.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Jonadab in, “Ka na ti-awla na ihkhun ah it aw. Na pa ih a ra lo veh tikah ‘Ka farnu Tamar ra sehla rawl i ra peseh. Ka hmuh theinak ahhin rawl cu ra tuah sehla amah rori in rawl i pe seh,’ tiah rak ti aw,” tiah Amnon cu a ti.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Curuangah Amnon cu a nater-aw ih a it. Siangpahrang David in a ra veh tikah, Amnon in, “Tamar ratter awla hitawk ka mithmuh ahhin sang ra tuah seh, cule amah rori in i pe sehla ka duh,” tiah a rak dil.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cule David in Tamar hnenah thu a cah ih, “Amnon umnak ah va feh awla rawl va tuahsak aw,” tiah a fial.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Tamar cu a va feh ih Amnon cu ihkhun parah a va hmu. Sangvut a lak ih a nawng ih Amnon ih hmaiah cun sang a tuah. Cule a sang cu a rawh ih,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> a rawhnak kheng sungin a suah ih Amnon cu a pek. Asinain a ei duh lo. Amnon in, “Midang hmuahhmuah cu khawlengah suak thluh hai seh,” tiah a ti ih an suak thluh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cule Tamar hnenah, “Ka ihkhun ahhin sang cu rak keng awla, nangmah kut rori in i ra baar aw,” tiah a ti. A rawhṭheh pektemi sang cu a lak ih Amnon ih hnenah cun a fehpi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Sang a pek laiah Amnon in Tamar cu a kai ih, “Ka hnenah rung it aw,” tiah a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cutikah Tamar in, “Asilo, ka it lo ding. Hranhram in cuvek thil mawilo cu i tuahter hlah. Cuvek cu Israel mi pawl ih tuah keelmi a si lo. Cubangtuk thil borhhlawh cu tuah hlah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ziangtin so mi hmaiah ka mit ka men ngam nawn ding? Cule Israel ram sungah nang cu mualpho in na um ding. Siangpahrang va tong sawn awla keimah ṭhit ding cu a lo el lo ding, tiah ka zum,” a ti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Asinain Tamar ih ṭong cu a ngai duh lo. Thacakdeuh a si vekin Amnon in Tamar cu a kaihrem ih a sualpi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cu ṭheh vete in Amnon in Tamar cu a mitkem ih a hua ngaingai. A hmaisa ih a rak ngainak hnakin a hnu ih a huatnak cu a nasasawn. Curuangah Tamar cu, “Tho awla tlan aw!” tiah a dawi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cutikah Tamar in, “Sihlah e, cuti menih i dawi asile ka thang i siatter zomi hnakin a sia sawn ding a si,” a ti. Sikhalsehla a thu cu Amnon in a ngai duh cuang lo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> A hnen-um pakhat a ko ih, “Hi nu hi ka mithmuh ah um hlah seh. A ban in innleng ah suahhlo awla sangka hren aw,” tiah a fial.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hnen-umpa in a suah ih sangka cu tawh a hren. Tamar cu a cuih san siangpahrang fanu, pasal nei hrih lo fala pawl ih an hruk ṭheumi korfual, a ban a saumi a hruk.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> A cuih a korfualpi cu a thlek ṭheh ih a lu ah vutcam a phulh-aw ih a hmai hup-aw in napi ṭap phah in a feh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> A ṭapa Absalom in, “Amnon in a lo hmuhsuam maw si? Ka farnu, ngui thlang aw, ziangahtile Amnon cu na ṭapa a si ve ih midang hnen khalah phuang hlah aw. Cutluk lawmmam ih riahsiat ding a si lo,” tiah a rak ti. Cutiin Tamar cu Absalom ih inn ah riahsia ninghang le lungleng in a um.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> A cuih thu cu siangpahrang David in a theih tikah a thin a heng ngaingai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> A farnu Tamar a kai ih a sualpi ruangah Absalom in Amnon cu a hua ngaingai ih a biak hman a bia duh nawn lo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Cuih hnu kum hnih ah Efraim khua kiangih Baal Hazor ah Absalom in a tuu pawl an hmul a metter. Cuih puai ahcun Absalom in siangpahrang ih fapa pawl hmuahhmuah ra tel dingin a sawm thluh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> A pa David hnenah a feh ih, “Siangpahrang bawipa, ka tuu pawl an hmul ka metter ih cutawkah na kuthnuai bawi pawl thawn na ra ve lo ding maw?” tiah a va sawm.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Siangpahrang David in, “Kan ra lo pei, ka fapa. Kan zate ih kan rat ahcun kan lo zonzaihter tuk ding,” tiah a ti. Absalom cun a hneek rero naón siangpahrang in feh ding a lungkim cuanglo ih, va feh aw, a ti ih Absalom cu thlawsuah a pek.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Sikhalsehla Absalom in, “Cuti asile ka u Amnon tal cu na thlah pei cu!” a ti. David in, “Ziangah so a feh ding?” tiah a ti.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Asinain Absalom in a leem rero ruangah a netnak ahcun David in Amnon le a fapa dang pawl cu Absalom hnenah cun a fehter. Absalom in siangpahrang ei ding tlak in rawl thawzet in a dar hai.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Cule Absalom in a hnen-um pawl hnenah, “Amnon hi zoh thup uhla zu mawng nawn ih a um tikah, ‘That uh,’ tiah thu ka lo pe leh ding. Ṭih hlah uh. Keimah ih thupek a si lo maw? ṭhukṭhun duh hlah uh. Ralṭha zetin tuah mai uh,” tiah a tiam.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Absalom ih thupek vekin a hnen-um pawl in Amnon cu an that. David ih fapa dang pawl cu zamrangin an laak an to ih an tlan thluh.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> An inn an thlen hlanah David hnenah, “Absalom in na fapa pawl a that thluh; pakhat hman an luat lo,” tiah thu a thang.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Cutikah siangpahrang cu a ding vukvi ih a riahsia in a hnipuan a thlek thluh ih zial parah a hlon aw. A kiangkap ih a ummi a hnen-um pawl khal in an hnipuan an thlek thluh ve.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Culai fangah David ih u Shammah ih fapa Jonadab cu a ra ih, “Maw siangpahrang, na fapa an zatein an that lo. An thah mi cu Amnon lawng a si. Amnon ih a farnu Tamar a sualpi vete khan hivek thil hi a tuah leh ding, ti cu Absalom ih mithmai ah na hmu thei ko a sisi.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Curuangah na fapa pawl an zatein an thi ti ih na theih mi thu cu zum duh hlah. Amnon lawnglawng a thi a si,” tiah a sim.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Cuih sungah Absalom cu a rak tlanhlo zo. Cule kotka kiltu ralkap pa in Horonaim lamzin ih tlangpar ihsin mi burpi an run kha a hmu. Zamrang in siangpahrang hnenah a feh ih, “Horonaim lamzin ih tlangpar ihsin mi tam nawn an rung ka hmu,” tiah a sim.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Cutikah Jonadab in, “Khi a rungmi pawl khi an ra ding ka lo ti ciami na fapa tla an si,” tiah a ti.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Cutiih a sim ṭheh vete in David ih fapa pawl cu an rung thleng. An ṭap ciamco ih David le a kuthnuai bawi dang pawl khal napi in an ṭap ve.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Absalom cu a tlan ih Ammihud ih fapa, Geshur ram siangpahrang, Talmai hnenah a relh. Cun David cu a fapa Amnon ngai in reipi a um.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Geshur ramah Absalom cu kum thum a um.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> David cu a mithi ngai a reh deuh thlang ih a fapa Absalom riangri a ngaizet."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Zeruiah ih fapa Joab cun siangpahrang David in a fapa Absalom a ngaizet, ti kha a thei.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Curuangah Tekoa khua ih a ummi nunau mifim pakhat kha a hnenih ra dingin a cah. Joab in a cuih nunau nu hnenah, “Mithi ngai bangin um-awter awla, mithi ngainak hnipuan hruk awla, na sam khal hriat loin um aw. Tikcu reipi mithi a ngai zomi nunau bangin um aw.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Cutiin siangpahrang hnenah va feh awla, ka lo tiammi thu hi va sim aw,” tiah a ti ih, a va sim ding mi thu cu Joab in a tiamta thluh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Nunau nu cu siangpahrang hnenah cun a va feh ih, upatnak pek in a lu leilung dai in a kun hnuah, “Maw siangpahrang, i bawm hram aw,” tiah a va ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cutikah siangpahrang in, “Ziang so na duh?” tiah a rak sut. Nunau nu in, “Bawipa, kei cu nuhmei farah ka si. Ka pasal in i thihsan zo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bawipa fapa pahnih ka nei. Asinain ni khat ah hramlak ah an unau an to-aw ih a ṭhentu an um lo ruangah pakhat in pakhat deuh kha a that.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cule bawipa, ka sungkhat pawl hmuahhmuah in, ‘Atuih a nunglaimi na fapa cu kan hnenah in pe-aw, a unau a thah ruangah amah kan that ding,’ in ti ciamco. An thah ngaingai a si ahcun kei cu fapa nei lo ka si thlang ding. Ka nunsan bikmi ka fapa neihsun cu an hlohralter ding ih, ka pasal cu hmin sawngtu fapa nei lo ah an canter ding a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Siangpahrang in, “Na inn ah va tlung aw. Na thu cu ka lo ruahsak ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cule nunau nu in, “Maw siangpahrang, ziangti ih na rel khalle mawhphurhnak cu keimah le ka innsang in kan tuar ko ding. Nangmah siangpahrang le na innsang parah mawhphurhnak zianghman a um lo ding,” a ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Siangpahrang in, “Zokhal in a lo hro asile ka hnenah ratpi awla a lo hnaihnok nawn lo ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Nunau nu in, “Maw siangpahrang, ka sungkhat pawl in a thimi ka fapa phulak tum ih, a nunglai mi ka fapa a thah an tum hi thil ṭha lo tuah tum an si ruangah, cutiih an tuahsuak lonak dingah Bawipa na Pathian hnenah thla cam hram aw,” tiah a dil. Siangpahrang in, “A nungmi Pathian hmin in ka lo kam a si: ziangti hman in na fapa cu an tuahmawh hrimhrim lo ding,” a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cutikah nunau nu in, “Maw siangpahrang, i zaangfah awla ṭong kam khatte na hnenah i simter hram hrih aw,” tiah a dil lala. Siangpahrang in, “Sim aw,” a ti.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cutikah nunau nu in, “Ziangah so hi bangtuk thil ṭha lo hi Pathian minung pawl ih parah na tuah? Na fapa cu a tlannak ihsin na kirter hrih lo ruangah atute ih na ṭongmi lala in na parah mawh a lo phurhter a si.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Minung cu kan thi cio ding; leilung parih an thletmi tidai cu khawm sal a theih nawn lo vekin milai kan nunnak cu khawm sal a theih nawn lo a si. Pathian hman in mithi cu a nuntersal nawn lo. Sikhalsehla siangpahrang cun ram sungah um ngam loih a tlanmi minung cu a kokir thei a si.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Maw siangpahrang, mi in in hro ruangah na hnenih ka ratnak a si ih, ka lo dilmi cu i tuahsak ding, tiah ruahsannak ka nei a si.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ka thusimmi cu i ngai hram pei ih, Pathian in a minung hnenih a pekmi ram ihsin ka fapa le keimah ci-mih in tumtu pa ih hnen ihsin in humhim ko ding, tiah ka ruat a si.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Maw siangpahrang, nang cu Pathian ih vancungmi bangtuk na si ih a ṭha le a sia ziang hmuahhmuah na thleidang thiam ruangah na thukamnak in i humhim ding tiah ka ruat. Bawipa na Pathian cu na hnenah um ringring hram seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cutikah siangpahrang in, “Thu pakhat ka lo sut ding ih diktein i sim aw,” a ti. “Bawipa, i sut ko aw,” tiah nunau nu in a ti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Cule siangpahrang in, “Hi thu ahhin Joab ih fialmi na si maw?” tiah a sut. Nunau nu in, “Maw siangpahrang bawipa, lei le van ko in ka lo sim: na thusuhmi leh ding cu ziangti hman in hrial a theih lo. Na hnaṭuantu Joab ih fialmi ka si. Amah in tuah ding le sim ding hmuahhmuah i tiam thluh a si.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hitiih a tinak cu nan thuhla hi tluang deuh seh tiah mer a duh ruangah a si. Maw siangpahrang bawipa, nang cu Pathian ih vancungmi bangin na fim ih thil a cangmi hmuahhmuah na thei thluh a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Nehhnu deuh ah siangpahrang in Joab hnen ah, “Na duhmi tuah sak dingah ka ruatcat zo. Va feh awla tlangval Absalom cu va ko awla hinah rak hruai aw,” tiah a ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Joab cu upatnak in David hmaika leilung ah a bok ih, “Maw siangpahrang bawipa, Pathian in lo thluasuah hram seh. Ka lo dilmi i pek ruangah hin na hnen ihsin mithmai ṭha ka ngah a si, ti ka thei,” tiah a ti.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Cule a tho ih Geshur ramah a va feh ih Absalom cu Jerusalem ah a rak hruai.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Sikhalsehla Absalom cu siangpahrang inn ih um lo dingin David in thu a pek. “A hmuh ka duh lo,” a ti. Curuangah Absalom cu amah ih inn ah a um ih siangpahrang hmaiah a suak dah hrimhrim lo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Absalom cu mi piangzet a si ih Israel ram sungah amah tlukih uar-mi zohman an um lo. A lu thlung ihsin a kebeu tiang soi ding pakhat hman a um lo.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> A sam a ṭha ngaingai ih a sau tuk le a rih tuk tikah kum khat ah voikhat tluk a met ṭheu. A sam cu siangpahrang ih cuai khainak in khai tikah pawng nga tluk a rit ṭheu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Absalom cun fapa pathum le Tamar an timi fanu pakhat a nei ih Tamar cu fala mawi ngaingai a si.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Absalom cu siangpahrang hmu loin Jerusalem ah kum hnih a um.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Cutikah amah ai-awh ih siangpahrang va tong dingah Joab a ko, a sinan Joab cu a ra lo. A ko sal naón Joab cu a ra thotho lo.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Cutikah Absalom in a hnen-um pawl hnenah, “Zohhnik uh, ka lo kiangte ih lo cu Joab ih lo a si ih barli sangvut tla a sungah a um a si. Va feh uhla meisa in va ur uh,” tiah thu a pek. Curuangah an va feh ih Joab ih lo cu meisa in an va ur.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Cule Absalom inn ah Joab cu a va tlan ih, “Ziangah so na hnen-um pawl in ka lo an ur?” tiah a va ti.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Absalom in, “Siangpahrang hnenih ka lo thlah theinak dingah hitawk ah ra dingin ka lo kawhnak a si. Siangpahrang hnenah va feh awla ka ai ah hiti in na va sim pei, ‘Ziangah so Geshur ram tan in hinah ka rat? Hitawk hnakin Geshur ramah um ningla keimai hrangah a ṭha sawn ding naón,’ a ti va ti aw. Cule siangpahrang ka ton theinak dingah i tawlrel sak aw. Mi mawh a si tiih i hmuh asile i that mai seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Joab cu siangpahrang hnenah cun a feh ih a va sim. Cule Absalom cu siangpahrang in a ko. A va feh ih siangpahrang hmaiah cun leilung dai in a va kun. Cutikah siangpahrang in Absalom cu a rak hnam."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cuih hnuah Absalom in rangleng le rang pawl a lei ih amah kilvengtu dingah ralkap sawmnga a ret.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Zingpitte in a tho ih an khawpi kotka lamzin kiangah a va ding ṭheu. Siangpahrang in ka thu i relsak seh, tiih a rami thuneitu pakhatkhat a ton tikah Absalom cun a ko ih, “Khuitawkin so na rat?” tiah a sut. Cule thuneitu pa in, “Bawipa, Israel ram cutawk khatawk ihsin ka ra ih cuih phun khaih phun ka si,” tivek in a ti ṭheu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Cutikah Absalom in, “Ngaita hnik, na thu hi nangmah ih neh ding tengteng a si. Asinain siangpahrang cun na thu hi a lo ruahsak lem lo ding.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Aw, hih ram ahhin thuṭhentu si ningla ka va duh so. Thuṭhentu si ningla thu a neimi le dil ding le sut ding a neimi pawl ka hnenih an rat tikah dikzet le felzet in ka relsak ding naón!” tiah a ti ṭheu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> A cu pa cu upatnak in Absalom hmai ih a ra kun tikah Absalom cun a kut in a hei dawh ih a kuah hnuah a hnam ṭheu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ka thu i relsak seh tiih siangpahrang hnenih a rami Israel mi hmuahhmuah cu Absalom in cuticun a rak ti ringring. Curuangah Absalom in an thinlung cu a kuai ngah thluh a si.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kum li a rei hnuah Absalom in siangpahrang hnenah, “Bawipa  Pathian hnenih ka thukamnak bangtuk in Hebron ah i fehter hram aw.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Geshur ramih ka um laiah Bawipai” hnenah, ‘Jerusalem ih i thlenter sal a si ahcun Hebron ah ka lo biak ding,’ tiah thu ka kam ta a si,” a ti.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Siangpahrang in, “Thlangamtein va feh aw,” a ti ih Absalom cu Hebron ah a feh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cutikah Absalom in Israel miphun pawl hmuahhmuah hnenah mi a thlah ih, “Tawtawrawt tummi aw nan theih tikah, ‘Hebron ah Absalom cu siangpahrang a si zo,’ tiah nan au pei,” tiah thu a cah thluh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Absalom ih a sawmmi minung zahnih khal amah thawn Jerusalem ihsin an feh ve. Absalom ih thusia ruahmi cu an thei lo. Thinlung thiangte in an feh ko.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Cule thawinak a pek rero laiah Absalom cun siangpahrang David ih thu a ron ṭheumi pakhat, Gilo khuami Ahithofel a cah ih thawinak a pek laiah cun a ra thleng. Cutiin siangpahrang an phiarnak cu a nasa deuhdeuh ih Absalom a thluntu khal an tam deuhdeuh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> David hnenah mi pakhat a ra ih, “Israel mi pawl ih thinlung cu Absalom lamah a her thluh zo,” tiah a ra sim.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cutikah David in Jerusalem ih a ummi a kuthnuai bawi pawl cu, “Absalom ih kut ihsin luat kan duh asile zamrangin kan tlan a ṭul. Zamrang uh! Culole hinah a ra thleng lohli ding ih in neh ding; khawsungmi cu ralnam thawn a sat ding ih kan ci in hmit thluh ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> “Asi, siangpahrang bawipa; na simmi hmuahhmuah cu kan tuah ko ding,” tiah a bawi pawl in an ti.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cutiin siangpahrang cu a pok ih a innsang le a kuthnuai bawi pawl hmuahhmuah in an thlun. Asinain siangpahrang inn kilkhawitu dingah a nusun pahra cu a taanta.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Siangpahrang le a minung pawl cu Jerusalem khawsung ihsin an suak tikah netabik inn ah an cawl.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> A kuthnuai bawi pawl cu a kiangah an ding ih siangpahrang kiltu Kereth ralkap pawl le Peleth ralkap pawl cu hmaiah an lan vivo. Gath ihsin a rak thluntu ralkap zaruk khal an lan.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> An hotu Ittai hnenah David in, “Ziangah so kan hnenah na feh ve? Kir sal awla siangpahrang thar hnenah um sawn aw. Nang cu ramdang mi na si ih na ram a taansantu na si.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> hittawk ah tikcu tawite sung lawnglawng na um ih ziangah so ka hnenah vakvai rero cun ka lo tuah ding? Cuih tlunah keimah khal khuitawk ah ka feh ding, ti ka thei-aw lo. Kir awla na ram minung pawl khal kirpi aw. Cun Bawipa cu na parah zaangfahnak a nei mi le rinsantlak si ringring hram seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Sikhalsehla Ittai in, “Maw siangpahrang bawipa, Pathian hmin salin ka lo kam: Nangmah na fehnak kipah, thihnak hmun a si khalle ka feh ve ko ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cutikah David in, “A ṭha! Cuti asile feh aw,” a ti. Curuangah Ittai cu a ralkap pawl le an innsang fanau pawl thawn a feh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> David ih dungthlun pawl an feh tikah misenpi cu nasazet in an ṭap. Siangpahrang David in Kidron Tivate a tan ih a minung pawl khal in an tan hnuah thlaler ramṭhing lamah an feh vivo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Puithiam Zadok khal a tel ih, Thukam Kuang phur phah in Levi mi pawl khal an tel ve. Mi hmuahhmuah khawpi sung ihsin an feh thluh hlanlo Thukam Kuang cu cutawk ah an ret. Puithiam Abiathar khal a tel ve.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Cule siangpahrang in Zadok hnenah, “Thukam Kuang cu khawsungah hei kirpi sal aw. Bawipa ih mithmai ṭha ka hmuh asile ni khatkhat cu i kirter sal leh ding ih hi Kuang le a umnak cu ka hmu sal leh ko ding.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Cun Pathian ih mithmai ṭha ka tong lo asile ziangti ṭha. Amah ih lungkim mi cu amah in tuah ko seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Cule Zadok hnenah cun, “Nangmah le na fapa Ahimaaz le Abiathar le a fapa Jonathan cu thlangamte in khawsungah vung kir uh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Cun nan hnenin thu ka theih hlanlo hramlak ramṭhing tiva tannak hmun ihsin ka hngak ringring ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Curuangah Zadok le Abiathar in Thukam Kuang cu Jerusalem ah an kirpi ih cutawkah an umta.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Cule David cu olif tlang ah ṭap phah in a kai. A ke lawngte in a kai ih riahsia in a lu a khuh aw. A thluntu hmuahhmuah khal an lu an khuh ih ṭap phah in tlang cu an kai.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Cun siangpahrang phiartu lakah Ahithofel khal a tel ih Absalom hnenah a ṭang a si, ti kha David an sim. Cutikah David in, “Maw Bawipa nangmah ih zaangfahnak in Ahithofel ih ruahnak pekmi cu thulolak ah cangter thluh hram aw,” tiah Pathian hnenah thla a cam.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> David cu tlangpar, Pathian an biak ṭheunak hmun a thlen tikah a rinsan zetmi, Arkhi hrin a si mi Hushai in a rak hmuak. Hushai in a hnipuan a thlek ṭheh ih a lu ah leivut a phulh aw.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Cutikah David in, “Ka hnenih na tel khalle na ṭhahnem lem lo ding.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Asinain khawpi sungah vung kir tahratin Absalom hnenah ‘Maw siangpahrang bawipa, na pa ih hnaṭuantu ka rak si vekin atu ahcun nangmah ih hnaṭuantu ka si thlang pei,’ ti awla Ahithofel ruahnak pekmi cu el ringring awla cuticun ka hrangah na ṭhahnem zet ding.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Puithiam Zadok le puithiam Abiathar tla an um ding ih siangpahrang inn ihsin thu na theihmi hmuahhmuah cu an hnenah than cingcing aw.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> An fapa Ahimaaz le Jonathan tla an hnenah an um ih hih an fapa pawl hnen ihsin thuhla na theihmi hmuahhmuah cu i rak theiter cingcing aw,” tiah Hushai cu a ti.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Curuangah David ih rualpa Hushai cu Jerusalem ah a kir ih Absalom a thlen zawng ah a thleng ve."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> David cu tlangpar ihsin malte a feh tikah, ruah lopi in, Mefibosheth ih hnen-um pa Ziba in a rak hmuak. Ziba cun laak pahnih a hruai ih laak pawl cun sang zawl zahnih, caar mi sabit rah bawr zakhat, thingrah lawh tharmi bawr zakhat le sabitti saphaw thawl khat an phur.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Siangpahrang David in, “Thil hi zatzat cu khuiah so na heih ding?” tiah a sut. Cutikah Ziba in, “Laak pawl cu siangpahrang ih innsang pawl to dingah an si; sang le thingrah pawl cu na minung pawl ih ei dingah a si; sabitti cu na minung pawl hramlakih an bang tikih an in dingah a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Siangpahrang in, “Na bawipa Saul ih fapa sin Mefibosheth cu khuiah so a um?” tiah a sut. Cutikah Ziba in, “Jerusalem ah a um; ziangahtile a pu Saul ih uknak cu a tuih ṭumah Israel mi pawl in ‘Ka hnenah in pe sal hmang ding’, tiih a zum ruangah a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Siangpahrang in Ziba hnenah, “Mefibosheth ih ta hmuahhmuah cu na ta an si thluh sokhaw,” a ti. Cule Ziba cun a lu a kun ih, “Kei cu na sal ka si ko. Siangpahrang nangmah ih mithmai ṭha a cotu si ringring hram ninglaw,” a ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> An feh vivo ih Bahurim khua an thlen tikah Saul ih sungkhat a si mi, Gera ih fapa Shimei cu David tong dingah mi camriam phah in a ra suak.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> David le a kuthnuai bawi pawl cu lungto in a deng hai ih ralkap pawl le a kiltu pawl in David cu an kulh ṭhepṭhep naón a deng thotho.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Shimei in David cu a cam ih, “Tlan aw, tlan zaang aw; laithat pa, mi sualral pa;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Saul ih uknak cu na long ih Saul ih sungkhat pawl tampi na thah ruangah Bawipa Pathian in atu-ah na parah phuba a la a si. Atu-ah Bawipa in na uknak cu na fapa Absalom hnenah a pek zo. Na cem a si, laithat pa!” tiah a cam ciamco.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cutikah Zeruiah ih fapa Abishai in siangpahrang hnenah, “Maw siangpahrang bawipa, ziangah so hih uico pa ih cam cu na tuar cuahco men? Ka va feh pei ih a lu ka va tan pei,” tiah a ti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Siangpahrang in Abishai le a u Joab hnenah, “Himi cu nannih thawn a seng lo. Pathian ih a fial ruangah i cam a si ahcun, ‘Ziangah so na cam?’ tiah zoso a ti thei ding?” tiah a ti.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cule David in Abishai le a kuthnuai bawi pawl hnenah, “Ka sungsuak ka fapa rori hman in a thah i tum a si ruangah hi Benjamin pa ih thil tuahmi parah mangbang ding zianghman a um lo. Bawipa in a fial a si ruangah a parah zianghman ti hlah uh, a duh tawkin i cam seh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bawipa in ka zonzaih harsatnak hi a run hmu pei ih, a tuih in cam rero can ai ah Bawipa in malza i sawm tla a si thei,” tiah a ti.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Curuangah David le a milai pawl cu an feh vivo. An dungin Shimei cun a thlun ih an fehnak tlangpar zinkap ihsin a feh ih a feh phah cun a cam vivo hai ih lungto le hnawmhne in a deng phah vivo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Siangpahrang David le a milai pawl cu Jordan an thlen tikah cun an bang hnephnep ih cutawkah David cu a cawl.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Absalom le a hnenih a ṭangmi Israel mi hmuahhmuah cu Jerusalem khua ah an lut ih Ahithofel tla a tel.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cule David ih rinsanmi a rualpa Hushai in Absalom cu a tong ih, “Siangpahrang a nun sau hram seh! Siangpahrang a nun sau hram seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cutikah Absalom in, “Na rualpa David ih milai na si nawn lo mawsi? Ziangah so amah na thlun lo?” tiah a sut.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hushai in, “Ziangtin so ka thlun thei ding? Bawipa Pathian ih a hrilmi le hi minung pawl le Israel misenpi ih an hrilmi lawng kei ka thlun ding a si. Na hnenah ka um ding.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Thungai ih kan ti ahcun, ka bawipa ih fapa rian loin zoso ka ren cuang ding? Na pa ih hna ka ṭuan vekin atu-ah nangmah ih hna ka ṭuan ding,” tiah Absalom cu a ti.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cule Absalom cu a her ih Ahithofel hnenah, “Na ruahnak in sim hnik! Ziangtin so thil kan tuah pei?” tiah a sut.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cutikah Ahithofel in, “Feh awla na pa ih inn, siangpahrang inn kilkhawitu dingih a taantami a nupisun pawl va ihpi aw. Cutiih na tuah asile a pa ih thin a hengter nasa zo tiah Israel mi hmuahhmuah in an lo thei ding ih na hnenih a ṭangtu pawl cu an ṭang sinsin ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Curuangah siangpahrang inn diphun parah deu an sak ih Israel misenpi mithmuh ah Absalom in a pa ih nupisun pawl cu a ihpi a si.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> A cuih san ahcun Ahithofel ih ruahnak cu Pathian ih ṭongkam ngaingai bangin an rak thlun. David khal in a rak thlun ih Absalom tla in a thlun ve."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Cun Ahithofel in Absalom hnenah, “Ralkap thawng hleihnih ka hril pei ih tuih zan tengteng ah David cu ka dawi ding.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> A baangzet laifangah le a thin a nauzet laifangah ka do pei. A thin a phang ding ih a milai pawl cu an tlan thluh ko ding. Culaitak ah siangpahrang amah lawng ka that ding.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Cule mothar a pasal hnenih a kir bangin a milai hmuahhmuah cu na hnenah ka run kirpi thluh ding. Thah na duh mi cu minung pakhat lawng a sisi. Midang pawl cu an him thluh ko ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cumi an theih tikah ruahnak ṭhazet a si, tiah Absalom le Israel hruaitu pawl in an ruat.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cule Absalom in, “Hushai ko hnik uh, anih simmi kan ngai ve pei,” a ti.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hushai cu a ra ih Absalom in Ahithofel ih simmi hmuahhmuah cu Hushai hnenih a sim ṭheh hnuah, “Ahithofel ih ruahnak hi kan thlun pei maw? Nang na ruahnak ziangtinso a si?” tiah a sut.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cule Hushai in, “Tuih ṭum Ahithofel ih ruahnak a lo pekmi cu a ṭha lo a si.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na pa David le a ralkap pawl cu raldo ṭhang cia an si ih tupi sungih a faate an lonmi savom vekin ṭihnung ngaingai an si ti cu nangmah in na thei thluh ko. Na pa cu raldo ṭhang cia a si ruangah zanah cun a ralkap pawl hnenah a riak lo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Atu fangah cun lungpuk sungah maw, hmun dangah maw a relh ding. Cule David in na minung pawl a nam ding ih cu vete in cuih thu a theitu hmuahhmuah in, “Absalom ih ralkap pawl cu an cem zo ee!” tiah an au ciamco men sawn ding.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cutikah cun kiosa vekih ṭih nei lo ral ṭha bik pa hman a thin a khur ko ding; ziangahtile Israel ram sungah cun zokhal in na pa cu raldo thiamzet a si ti an thei ṭheh ih a ralkap pawl khal raldo cakzet an si, ti kha an thei ṭheh a si.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kei ih ruahnak cu hiti in a si: Israel ram khatlam zim Dan ihsin khatlam zim Beersheba tiang Israel mi hmuahhmuah tifinriat kiangih vunnel zat a si mi cu kokhawm hai awla nangmah rori in raldonak ahcun ho aw.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Khuitawkih a um khalle David cu kan hawlsuak ding ih a theih man hlanah zan daitla bangin kan nam ding. Amah siseh a milai pawl siseh pakhat hman an luat lo ding.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Khua pakhatkhat sungih a luh khalle kan milai Israel pawl in hridai an keng pei ih, a cuih a relhnak khua cu lungto pakhat hman taang nawn lo tiangin horkuam ah kan dirsiat thluh ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cutikah Absalom le Israel mi pawl in, “Hushai ih ruahnak cu Ahithofel ih ruahnak hnakin a ṭha sawn,” tiah an ti. Absalom parih siatnak thleng dingah Ahithofel ih ruahnak ṭha cu Bawipa in a phelhsolh a si.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cule Absalom le Israel hruaitu pawl hnenih a ruahnak a simmi le Ahithofel ih ruahnak pekmi pawl hmuahhmuah cu Hushai in puithiam Zadok le puithiam Abiathar hnenah a sim thluh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cule Hushai in, “Atu zamrang uh! David hnenah thu hei cah uhla hramlakih tiva tannak hmunah cun zan khat hman rak riak nawn hlah seh. Amah siseh a milai pawl siseh, kaih le thah an tuar lonak dingah zamrangte in Jordan tiva tan in rak tlan hai seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Abiathar fapa Jonathan le Zadok fapa Ahimaaz cu khawsungah lut ngam loin Enrogel ihsin an hngak ringring. Hnen-um fala pakhat in khawsungih thil a cangmi le thuhla cu a va sim ṭheu ih cuih hnuah annih in siangpahrang David an va sim sin ṭheu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Asinain voikhat cu nauhak pa pakhat in a hmu hai ih cupa cun Absalom a va sim. Cutikah Jonathan le Ahimaaz cu an tlan ih Bahurim khua ih pakhat pa ih inn ah an va thleng. Cupa cun a inn kiangah khur pakhat a nei ih a cuih khur sungah cun an lut.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Cule cupa ih nupi in khur cu a khuh ṭheh hnuah zohmanih theih lo dingin a cuih khur parah fang a pho.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Absalom ih milai pawl an ra ih cu nu cu, “Khuiah so Ahimaaz le Jonathan an um?” tiah an sut. Anih in, “Tiva an hei tan zo,” tiah a ti. An hawl naón an hmuh lo ruangah Jerusalem ah an kir sal.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> An feh hnuah Ahimaaz le Jonathan cu khur sungih sin an suak ih David hnenah an feh ih thu hmuahhmuah an va sim. Ahithofel ih a phiarnak thu cu an sim ih David cu, “Zamrangte in pok awla tiva khatlam ralah feh aw,” tiah an ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Curuangah David le a milai pawl cu Jordan tiva an tan ih khawfing a cah tikah khatlam ralah an suak thluh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> A ruahnak pekmi an thlun lo kha Ahithofel in a hmuh tikah laak a to ih a khua ah a tlung. A innsang hnenih ro a cah hnuah amah le amah a awk that aw. Cuticun Ahithofel cu a thi ih a pa ih thlaan ah an phum.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Absalom le a ralkap pawl cu Jordan tiva an tan ih khatlam ral an thlen tikah David cu Mahanaim khua a rak thleng zo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> (Absalom in Joab ih ai ah Amasa cu a ralkap pawl hotu ah a ret. Amasa cu Ishmael mi Jether ih fapa a si; a nu cu Nahash ih fanu Abigail a si ih Joab ih nu Zeruiah ih unau a si.)",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Cule Absalom le a minung pawl cu Gilead ah an riak.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> David cu Mahanaim khua a thlen tikah Ammon ram Rabbah khua ih ummi, Nahash ih fapa Shobi le Lodebar khuami Ammiel ih fapa Makhir le Gilead ram Rogelim khuami Barzillai pawl in an rak hmuak.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kheng le tlak beel le ihphah le puan tla an rak keng. Cun David le a ralkap pawl ih hrangah sangvut sang, barli sang, vaiphawt, vaikan, be, mawṭol,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> khuaitizu, thawphat, cawhnawiha, tuu sa le cawsa pawl an rak keng ih ei dingah an pek. Hramlakah David le a ralkap pawl cu an bang ding ih an rilrawng in an ti a haal zet ding, ti an thei."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Siangpahrang David in a ralkap pawl cu a khawm ih a thawng le a za in a ṭhen ih anmah hotu bawi a ret vivo.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cule raldo dingah bur thum in a feh ter ih bur khatnak cu Joab in a ho; bur hnihnak cu Joab ih nau Abishai in a ho ih bur thumnak cu Git khuami Ittai in a ho. Siangpahrang bawipa in, “Keimah khal ka feh ve ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Cutikah annih in, “Kan hnenah feh ve hlah aw. Kanmah pawl kan tlan thluh, a si lole a hrek in that thluh a si hmanah kan ralkap pawl hrangah cun zianghman a dang cuang lo ding. Nangmah pakhat cu kannih pawl thawng hra tluk na si. Hi khua ah na um pei ih bawmtu in kuat thei le a ṭha sawn ding,” tiah an ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “A ṭha bik nan timi cu ka tuah ding,” tiah siangpahrang bawipa in a ti. Cule kotka kiangah a ding ih a ralkap pawl a thawng le a za in an feh cu a zoh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ralkap pawl hotu Joab, Abishai le Ittai hnenah, “Keimah zawnruat in Absalom cu tuahmawh hram hlah uh,” a ti. Ralkap hotu pawl hnenih David ih thupekmi cu ralkap hmuahhmuah in an thei thluh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> David ih ralkap pawl cu Israel ralkap pawl do dingah an feh ih Efraim Tupi sungah an do-aw ciamco.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Israel ralkap pawl cu David ih ralkap pawl in nasa zetin an neh hai ih a cuih ni ah ralkap thawngkul an thi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hmunkip le ramkip ah an do-aw ih hriamnam ih a thimi hnakin tupi sungih a hloral mi an tam sawn.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cule ruahlopi in David ralkap pawl le Absalom an tong aw. Absalom cu laak a to ih a laak cu sasuapi kung hnuai in a tlan ih thingṭek in Absalom cu a lu in a rak awk. A laak cu a tlan suak ih Absalom cu a ke leilung dai loin a thlai aw.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> David ih ralkap pakhat in Absalom cu a hmuh tikah, “Bawipa, sasua kung parah Absalom a thlai aw ka hmu,” tiah Joab a va sim.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cutikah Joab in, “Absalom e! Thungai maw? Ziangah so cutawkah cun na thah lo? That cila keimah hrimhrim in ngun tangka fanghra le taikhap pakhat cu ka lo pe ding naón,” tiah a ti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Sikhalsehla cupa cun, “Tangka thawngkhat i pek khalle siangpahrang ih fapa cu ka kutzung hman in ka dai lo ding. Siangpahrang bawipa in, ‘Keimah zawnruat in Absalom cu nan tuahmawh hram lo pei,’ tiah nangmah le Abishai le Ittai hnenih thu a lo pek cu ka thei thluh a si.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cun a cuih thu thlun loin Absalom cu that ningna siangpahrang in a thei leh thotho ding ih cutikah nang in i ṭan ngam ding ka zum lo,” tiah a ti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cutikah Joab in, “Nang thawn biak awk cu tikcu cem men a si,” a ti ih feipi pathum lak tahrat in sasuapi kungih a nungin a thlai aw mi Absalom ih thinhna ah a sun.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cule Joab ih ralkap pahra in Absalom cu an vun kulh ih an that.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cutikah an raldo bang dingah Joab in tawtawrawt a tumter ih a ralkap pawl cu Israel pawl an dawinak ihsin an rakir ṭheh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Absalom ruak cu an lak ih tupi sungih khur thukpi pakhat sungah an hlon ih a parah lungto vun liailiai in an peng. Israel ralkap pawl cu an tlan ih an inn ciarah an tlung.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Absalom cu a hmin sawngtu dingih fapa a neih lo ruangah a nunlai ah Siangpahrang Phairawn timi ah lungdawl pakhat a dawl. A cuih lungdawl cu amah ih hmin suangin hmin a sak ih atu tiangin Absalom Lungdawl tiah an tita.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Cule Zadok ih fapa Ahimaaz in, “Bawipa  Pathian in siangpahrang bawipa cu a ral kut ihsin a hum ruangah ka va tlan pei ih a cuih thuthang ṭha cu ka va sim pei,” tiah Joab hnenah a ti.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Joab in, “Asilo, tuihsun ahcun ziang thuthang hman na sim lo pei. Na than duh asile ni dangah na than leh pei; ziangahtile siangpahrang ih fapa a thih ruangah tuihsun ahcun na sim lo pei,” a ti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cule Ethiopia mi sal pakhat pa ih hnenah, “Feh awla na hmuh mi hi siangpahrang va sim aw,” tiah Joab in a fial. Joab ih hmaiah upatnak pek in a kun ih zamrangin a tlan.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Cutikah Ahimaaz in, “Ziangtiih a va can khalle hih thu cu ka va sim thotho ding,” tiah a ti. Joab in, “Ziangah so a cuih thuthan cu na duh? A cuih thu na than ruangah zianghman laksawng na ngah cuang lo ding,” a ti.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Ziang a si khalle ka feh thotho ding,” tiah Ahimaaz in a ti. Cutikah Joab in, “Cuti asile feh aw,” a ti ih Ahimaaz cu a feh. Ahimaaz cu Jordan Phairawn zin in a tlan ih Joab ih a thlahmi Ethiopia mi salpa cu a lan.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> David cu khawpi kotka pahnih karlakah a rak to. Ralvengtu pa cu khawpi an kulhnak hruang parah a kai ih kotka tlun zawn ah a ding. Khua a cuan ih mi pakhat a ra tlan rero kha a hmu.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Siangpahrang cu a ko ih a vun sim. Siangpahrang in, “Amah pakhat lawng asile thuṭha a rak keng a si ding,” a ti. Thu phurtu pa cu a ra nai deuhdeuh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Cule ralvengtu pa in midang pakhat a ra tlan rero kha a hmu lala. Kotka kiltu pa a vun ko ih, “Zohhnik, midang pakhat a ra tlan rero,” tiah a vun sim. Cutikah siangpahrang bawipa in, “Anih khal thuṭha a rak keng a si cu!” a ti.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ralvengtu pa in, “A hmaisa pa ih tlan zia ka zoh tikah Ahimaaz a bang,” tiah a ti. Siangpahrang in, “Ahimaaz cu miṭha a si ih thuṭha a rak keng a si cu,” a ti.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ahimaaz in siangpahrang hnenah, “Thu ṭha a si,” tiah a auh. Cule a hmaiah a bok ih, “Siangpahrang bawipa, nangmah a lo dodaltu hmuahhmuah tlunih nehnak a lo petu Bawipa na Pathian cu thangṭhat si ko seh,” a ti.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Siangpahrang in, “Absalom a dam maw?” tiah a sut. Cutikah Ahimaaz in, “Bawipa, na ralbawi Joab in i thlah tikah thu a hnok tukih ziang a cang ti ngaingai cu ka thei lo,” tiah a ti.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> “Khinah va ding hrih aw,” tiah siangpahrang in a ti ih Ahimaaz cu hlat nawn ah a va ding.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Cule Ethiopia mi pa cu a rathleng ve ih siangpahrang cu, “Maw siangpahrang bawipa, thuṭha ka rak keng a si. A lo dodaltu pawl ih tlunah Bawipa Pathian in tuih sunah nehnak a lo pek a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> “Absalom a dam maw?” tiah siangpahrang in a sut. Cutikah Sudan mi pa cun, “Maw bawipa, Absalom bangtuk in na ral pawl le a lo dodaltu hmuahhmuah cu si hram hai seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Cutikah siangpahrang David cu a riah a sia ngaingai ih kotka tlunih thlam sungah a hung kai ih a kai phah ah, “Maw ka fapa Absalom, Absalom ka fapa! Nangmah ih ai ah keimah sawn hi rak thih tak ding ee, Ka fapa! Maw Absalom, ka fapa,” tiah a ṭap."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Siangpahrang David cu a ṭap ringring ih a fapa Absalom ngai in a um tiah Joab an va sim.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Cule siangpahrang cu a fapa a thih ruangah mithi ngai in a um, ti kha David ih ralkap hmuahhmuah in an theih tikah an zate hrangah a cuih ralneh ni cu riahsiatnak ni riangri ah a cang.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ralkap pawl an kir tikah, ral an sung hnu ih ningzak ih a tlanmi ralkap bangin, khawpi sungah cun thawthaang nei loin an lut.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Siangpahrang cu a hmai a hup aw ih, “Absalom, ka fapa! Ka fapa Absalom ka fapa,” tiah napi in a ṭap zok rero.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cutikah Joab cu siangpahrang inn ah a feh ih a hnenah, “Nangmah le na fapa pawl le na fanu pawl le na nupi pawl le na nusun pawl ih nunnak a humhimtu ralkap pawl cu tuihsun ah an ning na zahter a si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> A lo duhdawtu pawl cu na hua ih a lo huatu pawl sawn cu na duh. Na ralbawi pawl siseh, na ralkap pawl siseh, na hrangah zianghman kan si lo, tihi fiangteón na langter zo. Tuihsun ahhin Absalom nungin kannih sawn hi thi nungla, na lung a kimzet ding, ti cu ka hmu a si.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Curuangah feh awla thathawhnak thu malte tal na ralkap pawl hnenah va sim aw. Na sim duh lo asile, Bawipa ih hmin salin ka lo sim: thaizing ah ralkap pakhat hman na hnenah an um nawn lo ding. Na no lai ihsin tuih ni tiang, na nun sungih na tonmi harsatnak hmuahhmuah lakah cumi cu na hrangah a harsa bik a si ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cule siangpahrang cu a pok ih khawpi kotka kiangah a va to. Cutawkih a um kha a minung pawl in an theih tikah a hnenah an ra thluh. A culaiah Absalom hnenih a ṭangtu Israel mi pawl cu an tlan ih an inn ciarah an tlung.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cule an ram pumpi ih an rel khawm bik mi cu, “Kan ral pawl kut sung ihsin siangpahrang David in in hum zo. Filistin pawl kut sung ihsin in luatter ih atu ah Absalom ih ruangah amah hman kan ram sungah a um nawn lo.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Absalom cu kan siangpahrang ah hriak kan culh naón raldonak ah a thi zo fawn. Ziangah so siangpahrang David cu kirter sal dingah zotal ih kan tawlrel lo?” tihi a si.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Israel mi pawl ih an rel reromi thu cu siangpahrang David in a rak thei. Curuangah puithiam Zadok le Abiathar tla cu Judah mi hruaitu pawl hnenah a thlah ih, “Siangpahrang bawipa a inn ih kirter dingah ziangah so nan taw a tlai?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> A sungkhat nan si ih amah ih titsa rori nan si. Ziangah so a kirsalnak ding thu ahhin hnufualtu bik nan si? tiah va ti hai uh,” a ti.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cule David in an hnenah, Amasa hnenah sim dingin hiti in a cah, “Nang hi ka sungkhat na si. Atu thok ihsin Joab ih ai ah ka ralkap hotu ah ka lo tuah ding. Ka lo tuah lo asile Pathian in i that seh,” a ti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cutiih David ṭongkam a um ruangah Judah mi hmuahhmuah ih thinlung cu, mi pakhat ih thinlung bangin, a her-aw thluh ih, “Na kuthnuai ih bawi pawl thawn ra kir sal uh,” tiah David cu an cah.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Curuangah David cu a kir ih, tiva khatlam ralih hruai dingah Gilgal ih a rami Judah mi pawl in Jordan Tiva in an rak hmuak.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cule culai fangah Bahurim khua ihsin Gera ih fapa, Benjamin mi Shimei cu siangpahrang David tong dingah Jordan lamah cun a vung tlan ve.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Shimei cu Benjamin miphun ihsin minung thawngkhat thawn an feh. Cun Saul innsang ih hnen-um a rak ṭuantu Ziba cu, a fapa hleinga le a hnen-um kul thawn, siangpahrang hlanah Jordan tiva ah a rak thleng.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tiva cu an tan ih siangpahrang ih innsang pawl khatlam ralih hruai bawmtu ah le siangpahrang ih ṭul mi hmuahhmuah tuahtu ah an cang. Siangpahrang in tiva a tan zik tikah Shimei cu a hmaiah a bok ih,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Maw siangpahrang bawipa, Jerusalem ihsin na feh ni ih thil ka tisual mi pawl kha cing hram hlah aw. Ka parih thinhengnak ah hmang hram hlah awla a ruah khal ruat nawn hram hlah aw.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bawipa ka sual ti ih ka theih ruangah sokhaw, saklam miphun hmuahhmuah sungah hmaisa bik ih a rung lo tongtu ka sinak cu!” tiah a ti.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cutikah Zeruiah ih fapa Abishai in, “Bawipa  Pathian in siangpahrang ih a hril zomi a cam ruangah Shimei cu thah tengteng ding a si,” tiah a hun ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Asinain David in Abishai le a u Joab hnenah, “Zo-inso nan ruahnak a lo sut? Ka hrangih hnaihnawhnak petu ah nan cang tum maw si? Atu-ah Israel siangpahrang cu keimah ka si ih tuihsun ah Israel mi pakhat hman thah an si lo pei,” tiah a ti.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Cun Shimei hnenah, “Zohman in an lo that hrimhrim lo ding,” tiah siatserh in thu a kam.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Cun Saul ih fapa sin Mefibosheth khal siangpahrang tong dingah a feh ve. Jerusalem ihsin siangpahrang a tlan ih nehtu bangin a ra kir sal hlanlo, Mefibosheth in a ke a kholh lo, a khahmul a met loih a hnipuan khal a sawp lo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Mefibosheth cu Jerusalem ihsin a feh ih siangpahrang hnenih a thlen tikah siangpahrang cun, “Mefibosheth, Jerusalem ihsin ka suah tikah zianghrangah na feh ve lo?” tiah a sut.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Mefibosheth in, “Maw siangpahrang bawipa, nangmah ih i theih vekin kei cu ka ke a zeng. Na hnenih feh ve dingah ka laak i dam sak aw, tiah ka hnen-um pa ka fial naón i rak bum a si.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Cuih tlunah na hnenah i rak zuarthlai fawn. Sikhalsehla nang cu Pathian ih vancungmi bangtuk na si ih a dik na timi cu tuah ko aw.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Thungai ih kan tile ka pa ih sungkhat pawl hmuahhmuah cu nangmah siangpahrang bawipa ih thah thluh tlak kan si, asinain na cabuai ih rawl ei thei dingah i rak tuah. Curuangah siangpahrang bawipa, na hnenih sin zaangfahnak khal dil ngam ding ka si nawn lo,” tiah a ti.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Cutikah siangpahrang in, “Na sim ding zianghman a um nawn lo. Saul ih leiram le thilri hmuahhmuah cu Ziba thawn nan ṭhen aw pei, tiah ka ruat cat zo a si,” a ti.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Mefibosheth in, “Bawipa, a zatein amah in nei thluh seh. Ka bawipa nangmah nungdamte ih na kir thei hi ka hrangah a tawk tuk zo,” tiah a ti.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Jordan tiva khatlam ralih siangpahrang hei thlah ve dingah Gilead mi Barzillai khal Rogelim ihsin a rung ve.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Barzillai cu a tarzet thlang; kum sawmriat a si. Milianzet a si ih Mahanaim ih siangpahrang a um laiah a rak cawmtu amah a si.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Siangpahrang in a hnenah, “Jerusalem ah i rak thlun awla ka lo kilkhawi ding,” a ti.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Asinain Barzillai in, “Reipi ka nung nawn lo ding. Ziangah so Jerusalem ahcun ka lo thlun rero ding?",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Kum sawmriat ka ti zo ih nun khal hi ka hrangah man a nei nawn lem lo. Ka ei ka in mi khal hi a thawtnak ka thei nawn lo ih nunau siseh mipa siseh hlamawi an sakmi tla ka thei nawn lo. Siangpahrang bawipa, nangmah ka lo zonzaihter lak men ding.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Cuti lawmmam ih na zaangfahnak co dingah ka tlak hrimhrim lo. Curuangah Jordan tiva ral malte tiang lawng ka lo thlahta pei.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Cule i kirter awla kan khua ih ka nu le ka pa ih thlaan kiangah ka nunnak cu cem ve men seh. Cun hinah ka fapa Khimham a um; siangpahrang bawipa, na hnenah fehpi awla a ṭha na tinak vekin run zoh aw,” tiah a ti.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Cutikah siangpahrang bawipa in, “Khimham cu ka fehpi pei ih na duhnak vekin ka zoh ding. Cun i dilmi pohpoh cu ka lo tuahsak thluh ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Cule David le a milai pawl hmuahhmuah cu Jordan tiva an hei tan. David in Barzillai cu a hnam ih thlawsuah a pek. Cuih hnuah Barzillai cu a inn ah a tlung.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Judah mi hmuahhmuah le Israel mi a hrek pawl in siangpahrang cu an kil ih Jordan tiva cu a tan hnuah Gilgal ah a feh. Cule Khimham khal in a thlun.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Cutikah Israel mi hmuahhmuah cu siangpahrang hnenah an feh ih, “Siangpahrang bawipa, na minung pawl siseh, na innsang le nangmah siseh, ziang ruangah so kan unau Judah mi pawl in anmah ih tabul vekin an lo ham ih Jordan tiva ral tiang an lo kil ringring?” tiah an ti.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Judah mi pawl in, “Ziangah so kan tuah lo ding? Siangpahrang bawipa cu kan phunpi a sisi. Ziangah so cuih ruangih nan thin a heng? Amah in rawl in dar ah maw nan ruat? Laksawng in ṭhen ah maw nan zum?” tiah an sawn.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Cule Israel mi pawl in, “Amah thawn phunkhat nan si khalle siangpahrang David hi nanmah hnakin ham theinak let hra in kan nei a si. Ziangah so in hmuhsuam? Thungai ih kan tile, siangpahrang kirter sal dingih a tawlrel hmaisatu cu kanmah kan si!” tiah an ti. Asinain Israel mi pawl ih ṭongkam hnakin Judah mi pawl ih ṭongkam cu a hrang deuh ngaingai."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Culai ah Benjamin mi Bikri ih fapa Sheba an timi pa pakhat a um ih amah cu mi hlotlauzet a si. Cule Sheba cun tawtawrawt tum tahrat in, “David hnenah covo kan nei lo, Jesse fapa ziang ṭhahnem lo! Israel mi pawl, tlungthluh uh,” tiah a au ciamco.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Curuangah Israel mi pawl cun David cu an tlansan ih Bikari ih fapa Sheba hnenah an feh. Sikhalsehla Judah mi pawl cun David cu an duh thotho ih Jordan tiva ihsin Jerusalem tiang an thlun.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> David cu Jerusalem a siangpahrang inn ah a feh ih a inn kilkhawitu dingih a retta mi a nusun pahra pawl cu a lak ih palik a kilter. An ṭulmi hmuahhmuah cu a pek thluh. Asinain an hnenah a it lo. An thih ni tiangin a dangte in a ret hai ih nuhmei bangin an um.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Siangpahrang in Amasa a ko ih, “Judah mi pawl cu hmun khatah ko thluh awla, tipsun ah hitawk ah ra uh,” tiah a ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> A tivek in Amasa cu a feh ih Judah mi pawl cu a ko. Asinain siangpahrang ih ni a tin ni ah Amasa cu a kir lo.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Curuangah siangpahrang in Abishai a ko ih, “Absalom hnak hman in Sheba in harsatnak in pe sawn ding a sihi! Curuangah ka ralkap pawl fehpi awla Sheba cu va dawi uh. Culo ahcun kulhmi khawpi hrekkhat a la pang dingih kan kut sung ihsin a luat pang ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Curuangah Joab ih milai pawl, Kereth mi, Peleth mi le ralkap dang pawl tla in Abishai cu an thlun. Sheba dawi dingah cun Jerusalem ihsin an suak.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cule Gibeon ih a ummi lungto tumpi an thlen tikah Amasa thawn an tong aw. Joab cu a ralthuam a hruk ih a ralnam cu a kawm sungah a than ih a taikhap ah a thlaih. Hmaiah a suak ih cutikah a ralnam cu a tla.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Cule Joab in Amasa hnenah, “Ka rual, na dam maw?” a ti ih hnam zik vekin a vorhlam kut in Amasa ih khahmul a hei kaih.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Joab ih ralnam a ken kha a thei lo ih Amasa cu a ralring lo. Curuangah Joab in Amasa cu a pum ah a sun ih a sungril pawl cu leilung ah a suak thluh. Sun saal hman ṭul loin hmakhatte ah Amasa cu a thi. Cule Joab le a nau Abishai cun Sheba cu an dawi vivo.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Amasa ih ruak kiangah cun Joab ih ralkap pakhat a ding ih, “David le Joab a ṭantu hmuahhmuah in Joab thluh uh,” tiah a au.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Lamzin laifangah Amasa ih ruak cu a thisen thawn ciah-aw in a um. Cumi a hmutu pohpoh cu an cawlhta ṭheu ruangah Joab ih ralkap pa in Amasa ih ruak cu lamzin ihsin hramlakah a dir ih puan pakhat a khuh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Cutiih lamzin ihsin a ruak an dirh hnuah Sheba dawi dingah an zatein Joab cu an thlun.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Israel miphun umnak ram hmuahhmuah pal phah in Sheba cu a feh vivo ih Abel Beth Maakah timi khawpi ah a va thleng. Bikri miphun pawl an kokhawm aw ih a cuih khawpi ahcun an hei thlun.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cun Joab ih ralkap pawl khal an thleng ve ih a cuih khawpi cu an kulh. An khawpi kulhnak phardawl cu tlu seh tiah Joab ih ralkap pawl cun phardawl hnuai ih leilung cu an lai ciamco. Cule phardawl lan theinak dingah a leng ihsin leilung in an khahsilh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> A cuih khawpi sungah cun nunau fim pakhat a um ih khawsungih phardawl parih sin, “Ngaihnik uh, ngaihnik uh! Joab cu hinah ratter hram uh; a hnenih thusim ka duh,” tiah a au.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Joab cu a va feh ih, “Joab na si maw?” tiah a rak sut. “Ka si,” tiah Joab in a ti. “Bawipa, rak ngaihnik aw,” tiah anih in a ti. “Ka ngai ko,” tiah Joab in a ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Cutikah nunau nu in, “Hlanlaipi ihsin, ‘Abel ah feh uhla thu cu a cat ding,’ tiah an rak ti ṭheu ih an ti vekin a cat ngaingai ṭheu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kan khua hi rem awknak khua le an zohsomi khawpi a si ih, Israel ram sungah hin mi kilkhawitu nu bangtuk a si. Ziangah so cubangtuk khua cu a siatsuah na tum? Pathian ih ta a si mi cu na siatbal ko sawh ding maw?” tiah a ti.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cutikah Joab in, “Asilo. Nan khawpi cu ka siatsuah hrimhrim lo ding.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kan tummi khal a si lo. Efraim tlangpar rammi Bikri ih fapa Sheba an timi in siangpahrang David cu a do ruangah a si. Cupa pakhat cu in rak pe uhla hih khua ihsin ka kir ding,” tiah a ti. Cule nunau nu cun, “Cupa ih lu cu phardawl tlun ihsin na hnenah kan rak hlon mai ding,” tiah a ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> A feh ih a ruahnak hmuahhmuah cu khawsungmi pawl a va sim. Sheba ih lu cu an tan ngaingai ih Joab ih hnenah phardawl tlun ihsin an vun hlon. Joab in tawtawrawt a tum ih, a ralkap pawl thawn a cuih khawpi cu an taan ih an khua ah an tlung. Joab cu siangpahrang hnenah Jerusalem ah a kir.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Joab cu Israel ralkap pawl hotu a si. Jehoiada ih fapa Benaiah cu siangpahrang David ih inn kilvengtu Kereth mi le Peleth mi pawl hotu a si.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Adoniram cu leiram an ṭuanter mi pawl hmuahhmuah hotu a si; cule Ahilud ih fapa Jehoshafat cu sungṭuan a si.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Sheva cu zung cazipi a si. Zadok le Abiathar cu puithiam an si ih,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Jair khuami Ira khal David ih puithiam pakhat a si ve."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> David a lal sungah kum khat hnu kum khat a peh in kum thum khengte paampi a tlung. Curuangah Bawipa Pathian hnenah David in a sut ih Bawipa cun, “Saul in Gibeon mi a thah hai ruangah Saul le a innsang pawl cu laithat an si,” tiah a ti.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> (Gibeon mi pawl cu Israel mi an si lo. Israel mi pawl in humhim dingih an rak tiammi Amor miphun pawl lakah a taangsun miphun fate pakhat an si. Asinain Saul in Israel mi le Judah mi pawl a ham tuk ruangah Gibeon mi pawl cu an ci in hmih thluh a rak tum a si.)",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Curuangah David in Gibeon mi pawl cu a ko ih an hnenah, “Nan hrangih ka tuah theimi ziangtal a um maw? Pathian ih miphun parah thluasuah vanluh tlung hram seh, tiah thlaza camtu nan sinak dingah nan parih thil ṭha lo an tuah zomi rem sal ka duh a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Cutikah annih in, “Saul le a innsang thawn kan ral awknak cu sui le ngun khal in a rem thei lo ding; Israel mi khal zohman a thah kan duh lo,” an ti. “Cuti asile nan hrangah ziangso tuah ningla nan duh?” tiah David in a sut.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Cutikah annih in, “Saul cun Israel ram sungah hin pakhat hman taang loin kan ci ih hmih thluh in tum a si.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Cu a si ruangah Saul ih tesinfa mipa pasarih in pe awla, Pathian ih hrilmi siangpahrang Saul ih khawpi Gibeah rori ah Bawipa Pathian hmaiah kan that hai ding,” tiah an ti. “Ka lo pe hai ding,” tiah David in a ti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Sikhalsehla Bawipa ih hmin salin David le Jonathan in thukam awknak an rak tuah zo ruangah, Saul ih fapa sin Jonathan ih fapa Mefibosheth cu David in a luatter.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Saul ih fapa pahnih - Aiah ih fanu Rizpah thawn an hrin mi Armoni le Mefibosheth cu a kai. Cun Saul ih fanu Merab le Meholah khuami Barzillai fapa Adriel ih hrinmi fapa panga khal a kai.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> An pasarih cu David in Gibeon mi hnenah a pek ih tlangpar ah Bawipa ih hmaiah an that. An pasarih in hmun khatah an thi. An thah tikcu cu ṭhal cem zawng, barli sangvut khawm hram an thawh tikcu a si.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Cutikah Aiah ih fanu, Saul ih nusun Rizpah in buri puan a lak ih lungpi parah ihphah ah a phah ih, rawl lak tikcu ih thokin fur ruah tlak hlanlo tiang an ruak cu sunih vate pawl in siseh, zanih ramsa pawl in siseh an ei lonak ding a kil ringring.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Rizpah ih thil timi cu David in a theih tikah,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> a feh ih Saul ih ruh pawl le Saul ih fapa Jonathan ih ruh pawl cu Gilead ih Jabesh mi pawl hnen ihsin a va lak. (Gilboa tlang parih Filistin mi pawl in Saul an thah sunah, Saul le Jonathan ih ruak cu Filistin mi pawl cun Bethshan ih senpi khawmnak hmunah an thlai. Cutawk ihsin Jabesh mi pawl in an va fir a si.)",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> David in Saul le Jonathan ih ruh pawl cu a lak ih Saul ih tefa pasarih an thahmi pawl ih ruh tla cu a khawm.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cule Benjamin ram Zela khua ummi Saul ih pa Kish ih thlaan ah Saul le a fapa Jonathan ih ruh pawl cu an phum. Siangpahrang David ih thupek bangtuk in ziang hmuahhmuah cu an tuah ṭheh. Cuih hnu lawngah an ram hrangih thla an cammi cu Bawipa Pathian in a sang a si.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Filistin mi le Israel mi pawl karlakah ral a tho sal. Cule David le a ralkap pawl cu an feh ih Filistin mi pawl cu an do. Cuti ih an do awk laiah David cu a baangzet.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cutikah mitum zet, mikei phun, Ishbibenob an timi pa cu ralnam phundang a pai ih, pawng hra a ritmi dar feipi kengin a ra ih David cu thah a tum.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Asinain culai fangah Zeruiah ih fapa Abishai in David cu a ra run ih Filistin pa cu a zon ih a that. Cule David ralkap pawl in an hnenah feh tahrat ih raldo ve nawn lo dingin David cu thu an kamter. “Israel mi hrangah tleunak na si ih in mihsan ding cu kan lo siang lo,” an ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Gob an timi hmunah Israel mi le Filistin mi cu an do-aw sal. Cutawkah Hushah mi Sibbekai in mikei vekih a tumzet mi Saf cu a that.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Cuih hnuah Gob ahcun Filistin mi thawn an do-aw lala. Cutawkah Bethlehem khuami Jair ih fapa Elhanan in Git khuami mitumzet pa, a feiko cu thiamtlang tia a si mi Goliath a that.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cun Gath ah do awknak a um lala ih cutawk khua ah raldo hiarzet mitumpi pakhat a um. Amah cun a kut ah kutzung paruk le a ke ah kezung paruk fingfing, a zatein zung kul hluanli a nei.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Israel mi pawl cu a zuam hai ih, cutikah David ih unau Shammah ih fapa Jonathan in cupa cu a that.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hi mikei vekih a tummi minung pali pawl cu Gath ih mitum pawl ih tesinfa an si ih David le a ralkap pawl in an that a si."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Siangpahrang David cu Saul le midang a ral pawl kut sung ihsin Bawipa Pathian in a luatter tikah Bawipa hnenih a sakmi hla cu a tanglam pawl hi an si:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bawipa cu ka Lungpi a si, Amah cu ka ralhruang le I tlentu a si.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ka Pathian cu ka beunak Lungpi le ka himnak a si. Amah in ralphaw bangin i hum ih, I ṭan ruangah ka him a si. Bawipa cu i runtu a si, I hum ih thi luannak ihsin i luatter.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bawipa cu ka ko ih, Ka ral pawl ih kutsung ihsin i luatter. Bawipa cu thangṭhat uh!",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Thihnak tilet cun i khuh ih, Siatnak tisuar cu ka par ihsin a luang.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Thihnak in a hridai in i ṭemih, Thlan khur in thang i kam.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ka thin a pit ih Bawipa ih hnenah ka au, Ka Pathian hnenah bomnak ka dil. A biakinn sungah ka aw a thei ih, Bomnak ka dilnak cu i run ngai.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bawipa cu a thin a heng ruangah, Leilung pumpi a hnin; Vanhram tiangin a hnin ṭheh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> A hnar sung ihsin meikhu a suah, A ka in mei-alh le meivam a suak.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bawipa in van cu a run hlip ih a rung ṭum, Khawdur tla cu a ke hnuai ah a ret.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cherubim to in a rung ṭum, Thli parah cuangin zamrang zetin a zam.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Khawthim sungah a zual aw ih, Khawdur sah zetin a kulh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> A umnak hmai ih tleunak sungin, Nimthlakau meivam a suak zohzo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cun Bawipa cu van ihsin khawri bangin a hrum, Cungnungbik Bawipa ih aw cu a khawk durdo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> A conkiang pawl a kap ih, A ral pawl an ṭhekdarh aw thluh. A nimthla a kau ih, A ral pawl an tlan thluh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bawipa in a ral pawl a kawkih, A thinheng in a hro hai tikah, Tipi thuanthum ih tawdeng cu a lang ih, Leilung ih hramṭohnak tiangin an lang thluh. A hnar ihsin a thaw a phawt tikah cun.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bawipa in van ihsin i run dawh ih i kai ngah, A thukzet mi tidai sung ihsin i suah ngah.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ka hrangih a cak tukmi ka ral pawl le Keimah i huatu pawl ih kut sungin i run zo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ka thin a pih laitak ah in do, Asinain Bawipa cun i hum a si.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Phannak hmun ihsin i hruai suak, Zalennak hmunah i thlenpi, Ka parih a lung a awi ruangah i hum a si.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Midik ka si man cu Bawipa in i pek a si; Mawh neiloin ka kut a fai ruangah i thluasuah a si.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bawipa ih in hmuhmi lamzin ka thlun; Ka Pathian hnen ihsin ka pial lo.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Amah ih daan hmuahhmuah ka thlun, A thupek mi pawl ka fehsan dah lo.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Sualnak cu ka hrial ih, Soiselnak um lo ka si kha a thei.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Midik ka si man cu Bawipa in i pek a si, Mawh neiloin ka kut a fai ruangah, i thluasuah a si.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Rintlak mi hnenah cun rintlak Bawipa na si. A famkim mi hnenah cun famkim Pathian na si.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> A thianghlimmi minung parah cun a thianghlim in na lang ih, Mi hrokhrawl pawl hnenah cun an sualnak hawl fetfettu na si.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Mi hnuai dor pawl cu na run ih, Mi hngal pawl cu na namthlak.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Maw Bawipa nang cu ka mei-inn na si ih, Ka thimnak hmuahhmuah na tleuter.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ka ral pawl do dingah thazaang i pek, An hauhruang pawl lan thei dingah cahnak i pek.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Hi Pathian ih thil tuahmi pawl cu an famkim a si, A thu pawl cu ziangtluk rintlak so an si! Beunak a hawltu hrangah cun, Amah cu ralphaw a si.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bawipa amah lawng Pathian a si, Pathian Amah lawng hi kan Lungpi a si.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Pathian cu ka beunak cak a si, Amah in ka lamzin a tluangter.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ka ke cu zukneng ke bangin a zamrang ih, Tlang parah khoh zetin i dinter.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Dar li hman nawp thei dingah, Amah in raldo i zirh.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Maw Bawipa, na runnak phaw i pek, I bawm ih mi mak ah i tuah.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Luat zetin ka ke i karter ih, Rilh bahnak ka tong dah lo.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Ka ral pawl cu ka dawi hai ih ka siatsuah thluh, Ka neh thluh hlanlo ka kir dah lo.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Ka vuakthlu hai ih an tho thei nawn lo; Ka ke hramah an bokta.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Raldonak hrangah cahnak i pek, Ka ral pawl ih parah nehnak i pek.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ka ral pawl cu ka hnen ihsin na tlanter; I huatu pawl ka siatsuah thluh.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Bomnak an dil naón zohman in an run thei lo; Bawipa an ko naón an aunak a let lo.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ka rial hai ih leivut vekah an cang; Ka pal hai ih lamzin ih ciarbek vekah an cang.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> I dodaltu hnenin i luatter ih, Miphun tampi tlunah uktu bawi ah i tuah; Ka theih dah lomi tla ka ukmi ah an cang.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Ramdang mi tla ka hmaiah an kuun ih, Ka thupek mi an theih vete in an thlun.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ramdang mi cu an thin a nau ih, An ralhruang sung ihsin khur thlohthlo in an ra suak.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Bawipa cu a nung! Lungpi cu thangṭhat uh, Pathian cu cawisaang sin uh, Ka rundamnak Lungpi cu.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Ka aiah phuba latu cu Amah a si, Miphun tampi ka hnuai ah a ret.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> I raltu pawl ih kutsung ihsin i luatter. Maw Bawipa, ka ral pawl ih tlunah nangmah in nehnak i pek; Mi siatsuahtu pawl ih kut ihsin i run zo.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Curuangah miphun zakip hnenah Bawipa ka lo thangṭhat ding; Na hmin thangṭhatnak cu hla in ka sak ding.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Pathian in a siangpahrang hnen ah nehnak a pek; A cat lomi a duhdawtnak cu, kumkhua in a langter; A hril ciami David le a tesinfa pawl hnenah."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Jesse ih fapa, Pathian ih a khaisan mi, Jakob ih Pathian in siangpahrang si dingih a hrilmi le Israel mi hrangah hla mawi zetzet a phuahtu David ih ṭongkam neta bik cu hibangtuk in a si:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bawipa ih thlarau in ka hnen ihsin a sim, A thu cu ka hmurka ah a um.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Israel ih Pathian cun a sim zo; Israel humhimtu in ka hnenah: “Dingnak le Pathian ṭihzah in, Mi a uktu siangpahrang cu,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Khawdur um lo zinglamih a tlang mi ni bangtuk a si, Ruah a han ih hrampi a tleutertu, ni bangtuk a si,” a ti.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> A pelh thei lo dingmi le, Kumkhua ih a hmunmi thukamnak in, Bawipa in thu i kam zo ruangah, Ka tesinfa pawl cu Pathian in a thlawsuah ding. Cumi cu ka saduhthah a si; Cumi cu ka nehnak a si ding, Pathian in a kimter tengteng ding.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Sikhalsehla Pathian a ṭihzah lotu cu, Nelrawn ih hlonhlo mi hling bangtuk an si. Kut lawngih tham theih pawl an si lo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Lak ding ahcun hreihriam le feipi hman a ṭul; Meisa ih ur thluh ding an si.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> David ih ralkap hminthang pawl cu hi pawl hi an si: Pakhatnak cu Takhemon mi Josheb Basshebeth a si ih “Mi Pathum,” timi lakah hotu a si. A feipi pakhat thawn ral minung zariat a do ih ṭum khatah an zatein a that thluh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Pahnihnak cu Eleazar a si ih “Mi Pathum,” lakih a tel ve mi a si. Amah cu Dodo ih fapa a si ih Ahoh hrin a si. Voikhat ah Eleazar le David in raldo dingih a khawm-aw mi Filistin mi pawl cu ṭih loin an dinhnawh ngam a si. Israel mi pawl cu an tlanhlo ṭheh.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Asinain Eleazar cu a umnak hmun ihsin a ṭang ih Filistin mi pawl cu a ralnam in a sat ciamco hai ih a kut a hit ṭheh ih a ralnam humnak hman pharh thei nawn lo tiangin a that. A cuih ni ah Bawipa in a cakzet mi ral a neh. Cuṭheh in Israel mi pawl cu a thi mi pawl ih ralthuam lak ding lawngah Eleazar ih hnenah an ra kir.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Pathumnak cu Harar mi, Agee ih fapa Shammah a si. Filistin ralkap pawl cu Lehi ah an khawm aw. Lehi ahcun bete lo pakhat a um. Filistin mi in Israel mi pawl cu an dawi thluh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Asinain Shammah cu lo sungih a dinnak hmun in a ṭang ih lo cu a kil ih Filistin mi pawl tampi a that. A cuih ni ah Bawipa in a cakzet mi ral a neh a si.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Lo ih rawlkhawm a cut zik thlang tikah Filistin ralkap pawl bur khat cu Refaim Phairawn ah an um. Cule “Mi Sawmthum,” sungih pathum pawl cu Adullam Lungpuk ah David hnenah an vung feh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> David cu ralhruang sungah a um ih, Filistin ralkap bur khat cu Bethlehem ah an um.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Cutikah David cu a lung a leng ih, “Aw, Bethlehem kotka kiangih a ummi tikhur ih tidai kha khuat khat talin in petu um hai sehla ka va duh ve,” tiah a hrum ruangro.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cule hminthang zet mi ralkap pathum pawl cun Filistin ral pawl cu an umnak ah an va nor ih tikhur ihsin tidai an khai ih David cu an pek. Sikhalsehla David in a in lo. Bawipa hnenih thawinak tidai ah a hmang.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Maw Bawipa, hi tidai cu ziangtinso ka in thei ding?. An nunnak pek ngam ih an khaimi a si ruangah hi tidai ka in ahcun ka ralkap pathum ih thisen in ka bang ding,” a ti. Curuangah a cuih tidai cu in loin thawinakah a thlet. A tlunih porh tlak hnaṭuanmi pawl cu hminthang ralkap pathum ih tuah mi an si.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Joab ih nau Zeruiah ih fapa, Abishai cu “Mi Sawmthum,” ih hotu a si. Voikhat cu a feipi pakhat thawn ral zathum a do ih a that thluh. Curuangah “Mi Sawmthum,” sungah a hmin a thang ngaingai.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Sawmthum sungih hminthang bik a si ruangah an hotu ah a cang. Asinain “Mi Pathum,” pawl cu a tluk lo.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cun Kabzeel khuami, Jehoiada ih fapa, Benaiah cu ralkap hminthangzet le raldonak ih ralṭhazet a si. Moab ralkap hminthangzet pahnih tla a that. Vur a tlak sun ni khat ah khur sungah luhhnawh tahratin kiosa pakhat tla a that.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Cule Izipt mi pa mi tumzet, feipi a kengtu pa tla a that. Benaiah cun talhtum thawn a nam ih Izipt pa ih kut sungih sin feipi cu a long ih amah ih feipi lala cun a thatta.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Benaiah ih ralṭhat zia cu cubangtuk a si. Amah cu “Mi Sawmthum,” lakih pakhat a si.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Sawmthum lakah mi hleice a si. Asinain pathum pawl cu a tluk lo. David in amah kilvengtu pawl hotu ah a ret.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hminthang “Sawmthum,” sungih a telmi midang pawl cu a tanglam pawl hi an si: Joab ih nau Asahel, Bethlehem ihsin Dodo ih fapa Elhanan,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Harod ihsin Shammah, Harod ihsin Elika,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Pelet ihsin Helez, Tekoa ihsin Ikkesh ih fapa Ira,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Anathoth ihsin Abiezer, Hushah ihsin Mebunnai,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ahoh ihsin Zalmon, Netofah ihsin Maharai,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Netofah ihsin Baanah ih fapa Heleb, Benjamin ram Gibeah ihsin Ribai ih fapa Ittai,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Pirathon ihsin Benaiah, Gaash kiang phairawn ram ihsin Hiddai,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Arabah ihsin Abialbon, Bahurim ihsin Azmaveth,",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Shaalbon ihsin Eliahba, Jashen ih fapa pawl, Jonathan,",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Harar ihsin Shammah, Harar ihsin Sharar ih fapa Ahiam,",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Maakah ihsin Ahasbai ih fapa Elifelet, Gilo ihsin Ahithofel ih fapa Eliam,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Karmel ihsin Hezro, Arab ihsin Paarai,",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Zobah ihsin Nathan ih fapa Igal, Gad ihsin Bani,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Ammon ihsin Zelek, Beeroth ihsin Joab ih hriamnam phurtu Zeruiah ih fapa Naharai.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Jattir ihsin Ira. Jattir ihsin Gareb,",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Hit mi pa Uriah. An zateón ralkap hminthang sawmthum le pasarih an um."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Israel parah Bawipa cu a thin a heng sal ih an hnenih harsatnak thlenter dingah David cu, “Feh awla Israel le Judah mi pawl mipum siar aw,” tiah a forh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Curuangah David in a ralkap hotu ralbawi Joab cu a ko ih, “Na kuthnuai ih bawi pawl thawn kan ram khatlam deng Dan ihsin khatlam deng Beersheba tiang feh awla Israel miphun hmuahhmuah mipum va siar aw. Minung ziangzat an um ti a theih ka duh,” tiah a ti.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Asinain Joab in, “Maw siangpahrang bawipa, Bawipa na Pathian in Israel mi pawl cu atu hnakin a let za in pungzaiter hram sehla na nunsung ah cumi cu hmu dingin run tuah hram seh. Asinain maw siangpahrang bawipa, ziangah so mipum siar cu na duh?” a ti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Sikhalsehla siangpahrang in Joab le a kuthnuai ih bawi pawl cu a thupek mi vekin a thlunter ih curuangah an suak ih Israel mi siar dingah an feh.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Jordan tiva an tan ih Gad ram sung phairawn ih a ummi Aroer khawpi ih thlanglam ah an riak. Cutawk ihsin Jazer ah an hung feh ih,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Gilead le Hit ramsung Kadesh ah an hung thleng. Cule Dan an hung thlen hnuah cutawk ihsin nitlaknak lamah an her-aw ih Sidon an va thleng.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Cuih hnuah ralhruang ih kulh mi khawpi ṭai-ar khua ah an vung feh ih cutawk ihsin Hiv khawpi pawl le Kanaan khawpi pawl ah an thleng. A netabik ah Judah ram thlanglam bikih a ummi Beersheba khua an thleng.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Cuticun an ram pumpuluk an tlawng ṭheh ih thla kua le ni kul an rei hnuah Jerusalem khua ah an kir.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Siangpahrang hnenah, “Raldo dingin hriamnam a keng theitu mipa cu Israel ram ah thawng zariat an um ih, Judah ram ah thawng zanga an um,” tiah an va sim.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Sikhalsehla cutiih mipum siarnak an tuah ngah tikah, David cu a thin a nuam lo ngaingai ih Bawipa ih hnenah, “Thil sualzet ka tuah zo a si. Maw Bawipa, ka sualnak i ngaidam hram aw. Aatthlakza ka tuah a si,” tiah a dil.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Cutikah David ih puithiam a ṭuantu, profet Gad hnenah Bawipa ih ṭongkam cu a ra thleng ih, “David ih hril dingah thil pathum ka pek. Pakhatkhat hril-aw sehla a parah ka kimter ding, tiah David va sim aw,” a ti. A thaizing David a thawh tikah,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> profet Gad cu a hnenah a ra thleng ih Bawipa ih ṭongmi cu a ra sim. “Hi pathum lakah khuiso na hril ding? Na uk sung hmuahhmuah ah paam kum thum sung thlen maw? Asilole na ral pawl hnen ihsin thlathum sung tlan rero maw? Asilole na ram sungih ni thum sung pulhnat thlen so na hril sawn ding? ṭhatein ruatta awla, Bawipa hnenih va sim kir dingah thu i let aw,” tiah a ti.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Cutikah David in, “Ka mang a bangtuk aw! Sikhalsehla minung kut sungih thlen hnak cun Bawipa ih kut sungah thleng ninglaw! Ziangahtile Bawipa cu mi zaangfah thiam a si,” a ti.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Curuangah Bawipa in Israel ram sungah a cuih zing ih thokin a tiamkammi tikcu tiang pulhnat a tlunter. Israel ram pumpuluk ah Israel mi thawng sawmsarih an thi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Cule Bawipa ih vancungmi in Jerusalem khua a siatsuah zik tikah, Israel mi hrem nawn lo dingin Bawipa cu a thinlung a thleng-aw sal ih mi a that rerotu vancungmi hnenah cun, “Bang aw! Tawk thlang seh,” tiah a ti. Culai fangah vancungmi cu Jebus mi Araunah ih fang cilnak puum kiangah a um.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Cule Israel mi a that rerotu vancungmi cu David in a hmuh tikah Bawipa ih hnenah, “A mawhtu cu keimah ka si. Thilsual a tuahtu cu keimah ka si. Hi mizonzai na milai pawl in ziang sualnak so an tuah? Na hremnak cu keimah le ka innsang parah thleng sawnseh,” tiah a ti.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> A cuih ni ah profet Gad cu David hnenah a va feh ih, “Araunah ih fang cilnak puum ah hung feh awla Bawipa ih hrangah biakṭheng hung dawl aw,” tiah a ti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Gad ih simmi Bawipa ih thupek cu David in a ngai ih a hung feh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Cule Araunah in a vun zoh tikah siangpahrang bawipa le a kuthnuai ih bawi pawl an hun rero kha a vun hmu. Cuvete in a feh ih David ih hmaiah leilung dai in a kun ih,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Maw siangpahrang bawipa, ziangah so kei na salpa hi i ra len?” tiah a rak sut. Cutikah David in, “Mi tampi an thihnak pulhnat hi a reh theinak dingah na fang cilnak puum hi lo lei tahratin Bawipa ih hrangih biakṭheng dawl ka duh ruangah ka ra a si,” tiah a ti.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Araunah in, “Maw siangpahrang bawipa, na ṭul mi hmuahhmuah lak awla Bawipa ih hnenah cun pe aw. Biakṭheng parih mei-ur thawinak hrangah hinah cawcang an um. Cun tih ding zanthing ah caw hngawngkol le fang cilnak zial pawl an um,” a ti.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Araunah in a neihmi hmuahhmuah cu siangpahrang hnenah a pek ih, “Bawipa  na Pathian in na thawinak cu lo sang hram seh,” tiah a ti.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Asinain siangpahrang bawipa in, “Asilo, a man ka lo pe thluh ding. A man zianghman ka pek lomi cu Bawipa ka Pathian hnenih thawinak ah ka pe lo ding,” a ti. Cule Araunah ih puum le cawcang cu ngun tangka sawmnga in a lei.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Cutawkah biakṭheng cu a dawl ih mei-ur thawinak le remnak thawinak cu Bawipa ih hnenah a pek. Cuticun Bawipa in a thlacamnak cu a ngai ih Israel ram sungih pulhnat cu a reh."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;